mmary%22%3A%22With%20her%20last%20name%20being%20Pretzel%2C%20she%20has%20been%20offered%20jobs%20solely%20on%20her%20unique%20last%20name.%20While%20it%20is%20odd%2C%20she%20and%20her%20family%20love%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Jillian%20Pretzel)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22We've%20visited%2050%20states%20and%2091%20countries%20and%20almost%20always%20choose%20hotels%20over%20Airbnbs.%20Here's%20why.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22John%20and%20Beverly%20Martin%20on%20a%20rickshaw%20in%20India%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cfb60bf533b039a884c762%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221120%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJohn%20and%20Beverly%20Martin%2C%2060%2C%20are%20known%20as%20the%20%26quot%3BRetirement%20Travelers.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20John%20and%20Beverly%20Martin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ERetirees%20John%20and%20Beverly%20Martin%2C%2060%2C%20sold%20their%20Florida%20home%20in%202019%20to%20travel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIn%202021%2C%20they%20began%20circling%20the%20globe%2C%20traveling%20to%20over%2091%20countries.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey%20used%20to%20default%20to%20Airbnbs%20but%20now%20prefer%20hotels%20for%20their%20consistency%20and%20free%20breakfast.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20John%20Martin%2C%20who%20previously%20worked%20in%20the%20aluminum%20industry%2C%20and%20his%20wife%20Beverly%2C%20both%2060%2C%20who%20have%20been%20traveling%20the%20United%20States%20and%20the%20world%20since%202019.%20The%20conversation%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJohn%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20retired%20at%2055%20at%20the%20end%20of%202019.%20Initially%2C%20we