20our%20perspective.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20so%20many%20years%2C%20we%20were%20caught%20up%20in%20the%20rat%20race.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETheir%20extensive%20travel%20experience%20has%20changed%20their%20initial%20preference%20for%20Airbnbs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22John%20and%20Beverly%20Martin%20looking%20out%20a%20train%20window%20onto%20a%20Norwegian%20forest.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cfb6fff533b039a884c877%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22739%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Martins%20traveling%20through%20Norway.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20John%20and%20Beverly%20Martin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJohn%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe%20didn't%20even%20consider%20hotels%20at%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBeverly%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20When%20we%20started%2C%20our%20initial%20thought%20was%20Airbnb%20was%20the%20best%20option.%20It%20seemed%20the%20most%20affordable.%20And%20watching%20other%20nomads%20on%20social%20media%20and%20YouTube%2C%20it's%20a%20very%20popular%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJohn%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20After%20about%20a%20year%2C%20we%20started%20noticing%20we%20could%20stay%20at%20hotels%20for%20a%20similar%20price%20to%20the%20Airbnbs.%20It%20wasn't%20that%20much%20of%20a%20difference.%20We%20didn't%20have%20a%20terrible%20time%20with%20Airbnbs%2C%20but%20just%20found%20them%20to%20be%20not%20consistent.%20About%20half%20the%20time%20they%20were%20amazing%2C%20but%20the%20other%20half%20we%20had%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJohn%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThere%20was%20one%20host%20in%20Albania%20who%20wanted%20us%20to%20switch%20rooms%20last%20minute%2C%20but%20the%20new%20rooms%20were%20next%20to%20jackhammers%20at%20a%20construction%20site.%20We%20had%20a%20host%20in%20Bulgaria%20who%20asked%20us%20to%20cancel%20at%20the%20last%20minute%2C%20which%20we%20didn't%20feel%20comfortable%20with.%20It%20was%20just%20little%20things%20that%20started%20to%20add%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBeverly%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Not%20all%20of%20them%20were%20bad%20%E2%80%94%20we%20had%20some%20amazing%20experiences%2C%20like%20a%20container%20home%20in%20Costa%20Rica%20and%20an%20artists'%20retreat%20in%20Guatemala.%20But%20some%20other%20people%20who%20travel%20like%20us%20will%20stay%20for%20a%20month%20in%20a%20place%20to%20get%20a%2010%25%20discount.%20We%20don't%20do%20stays%20like%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJohn%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20started%20checking%20prices%20and%20realized%2C%20you%20know%2C%20we're%20not%20a%20big%20family%20that%20needs%20to%20spread%20out.%20We're%20not%20staying%20in%20places%20for%20months%20at%20a%20time.%20We%20typically%20stay%20in%20one%20location%20around%20four%20to%20seven%20days.%20For%20our%20type%20of%20travel%2C%20getting%20hit%20with%20a%20%24250%20cleaning%20fee%20for%20just%20a%20few%20nights%20didn't%20make%20sense.%20It%20was%20like%3A%20Wait%20a%20second%2C%20we%20could%20pay%20this%20at%20a%20hotel%20%E2%80%94%20and%20get%20a%20free%20breakfast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJohn%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20only%20eat%20two%20meals%20a%20day.%20So%20we%20get%20one%20of%20our%20meals%20paid%20for%20with%20a%20great%20breakfast.%20And%20with%20an%20Airbnb%2C%20you%20still%20have%20to%20go%20to%20the%20grocery%20store%2C%20bring%20stuff%20back%2C%20and%20cook.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22John%20Martin%20walking%20along%20the%20rocks%20in%20Santorini.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cfb73da610a9069d5a0f6a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22718%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJohn%20Martin%20in%20Santorini%2C%20Greece.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20John%20and%20Beverly%20Martin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBeverly%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We've%20been%20using%20credit%20card%20points%20to%20stay%20at%20Hyatts