2%3Ecashing%20in%20as%20an%20influencer%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20something%20she%20uses%20English%20muffins%20to%20demonstrate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20couple%20of%20weeks%20ago%2C%20she%20posted%20a%20video%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40bethennyfrankel%2Fvideo%2F7330610222832028971%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETikTok%3C%2Fa%3E.%20With%20her%20trademark%20mix%20of%20fast-talking%20brash%20honesty%20and%20humor%2C%20she%20slammed%20the%20Thomas'%20English%20muffin%20sleeve.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCan%20we%20improve%20this%20package%3F%26quot%3B%20Frankel%20ranted.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20really%20from%20the%20dark%20ages.%20Fred%20Flinstone%20is%20eating%20an%20English%20muffin%20like%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20return%2C%20Thomas'%20sent%20her%20a%20box%20of%20products%2C%20including%20blueberry%20English%20muffins%2C%20which%20she%20said%20her%2013-year-old%20daughter%20loves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20doesn't%20matter%20if%20I%20hate%20on%20or%20love%20on%2C%20people%20are%20into%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20her%20cutting%20takes%20and%2C%20at%20times%2C%20brutally%20truthful%20opinions%2C%20people%20can't%20seem%20to%20stop%20talking%20about%20%E2%80%94%20and%20following%20%E2%80%94%20Frankel.%20They%20have%20been%20for%20the%20past%2016%20years%20since%20she%20first%20hit%20the%20public%20eye%20as%20the%20outsider%20on%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwho-is-jenna-lyons-real-housewives-j-crew-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Real%20Housewives%20of%20New%20York%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20she%20left%20for%20good%20in%202019.%20(For%20about%20a%20year%2C%20she's%20been%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vanityfair.com%2Fhollywood%2F2023%2F10%2Freal-housewives-bravo-reckoning%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epublic%20feud%20with%20the%20show's%20network%2C%20Bravo%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20went%20on%20a%20quest%20to%20unionize%20reality%20TV%20stars%20last%20summer.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20she's%20earning%20seven%20figures%20annually%20from%20social%20media%20%E2%80%94%20more%20than%20she%20earned%20per%20year%20on%20Housewives%2C%20she%20said.%20(She's%20never%20disclosed%20how%20much%20she%20made%20on%20the%20show%2C%20but%20said%20it%20was%20millions.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20her%20first%20full%20year%20of%20embracing%20the%20status%20of%20%26quot%3Binfluencer%2C%26quot%3B%20Frankel%20earned%20%243.2%20million%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finfluencers-brand-deals-ugc-slack-user-generated-content-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eendorsement%20deals%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20according%20to%20documents%20reviewed%20by%20BI.%20Brands%20like%20L'Oreal%20and%20Dunkin'%20pay%20five%20or%20six%20figures%20for%20promotion%20by%20Frankel%20on%20TikTok%20and%20Instagram.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20has%203.3%20million%20and%201.6%20million%20followers%20on%20the%20platforms%2C%20respectively%2C%20up%20from%202.4%20million%20and%20320%2C000%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ein%20February%202022%2C%20before%20she%20started%20posting%20so%20regularly%2C%20per%20data%20from%20analytics%20firm%20SocialBlade.%20Across%20all%20social%20platforms%2C%20her%20content%20receives%2057.48%25%20positive%20sentiment%20%E2%80%94%20more%20than%20the%20reality%20star%20average%20of%2040%25%20to%2045%25%2C%20according%20to%20influencer%20marketing%20platform%20Captiv8.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EBethenny%20Frankel%2C%20the%20%26quot%3Baccidental%20influencer%26quot%3B%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20her%20path%20to%20that%20success%20through%20reality%20TV%2C%20she%20calls%20herself%20an%20%26quot%3Baccidental%20influencer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrankel%20has%20an%20over-the-top%20personality%20and%20prides%20herself%20in%20authenticity%2C%20two%20trademarks%20of%20today's%20TikTok%20set.%20That%20appears%20to%20have%20helped%20the%2053-year-old%20in%20her%20career%20pivot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20secret%2C%20she%20says%2C%20is%20that%20she%20wasn't%20looking%20to%20become%20an%20influencer.%20She%20was%20just%20learning%20how%20to%20do%20her%20own%20makeup%20after%20years%20of%20having%20it%20done%20for%20her.%20After%20watching%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-influencer-bianca-ingrosso-built-multimillion-dollar-beauty-brand-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebeauty%20videos%20online%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20she%20began%20posting%20her%20own%20in%202022.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221750%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bethenny%20Frankel.%20atdrugstore%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cfcd07f533b039a884df8d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221250%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBethenny%20Frankel%20often%20skewers%20expensive%20products%2C%20favoring%20drugstore%20brands.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Bethenny%20Frankel%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMuch%20of%20her%20content%20hypes%20drugstore%20brands%20and%20skewers%20expensive%20alternatives.%20La%20Mer's%20Cr%C3%A8me%20de%20la%20Mer%20(which%20retails%20for%20%24200%20for%20one%20oz)%20and%20Nivea's%20signature%20Creme%20(about%20%2412%20for%2016%20oz)%20are%20pretty%20interchangeable%2C%20she%20says%20in%20one%20video.%20There's%20very%20little%20editing%20and%20a%20messy%20quality%20to%20her%20posts%3B%20in%20a%20recent%20upload%2C%20for%20example%2C%20she%20had%20a%20piece%20of%20fluff%20stuck%20on%20her%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20more%20authentic%20you%20are%20and%20the%20less%20desperate%20you%20are%20%E2%80%94%20if%20you're%20doing%20things%20you're%20passionate%20about%20and%20being%20honest%2C%20things%20will%20just%20walk%20in%20the%20door%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20didn't%20take%20long%20for%20the%20clips%20to%20catch%20the%20attention%20of%20big%20companies.%20In%20April%202022%2C%20she%20scored%20her%20first%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-reach-out-to-brands-influencer-collaboration-post-email%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebrand%20deal%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20CoverGirl%2C%20her%20representatives%20said.%20Since%20then%2C%20she's%20expanded%20beyond%20beauty%2C%20reviewing%20grocery%20store%20finds%20and%20commenting%20on%20pop%20culture.%20She%20posts%20dozens%20of%20videos%20a%20week%20across%20TikTok%2C%20Instagram%2C%20and%20YouTube%20%E2%80%94%20and%20she's%20approached%20social%20media%20with%20business%20savvy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20brands%20want%20to%20use%20her%20existing%20content%20in%20promotions%2C%20for%20example%2C%20she%20requires%20them%20to%20pony%20up.%20When%20they%20ask%20her%20to%20review%20products%2C%20she%20isn't%20willing%20to%20accept%20free%20stuff%20or%20shill%20something%20she%20doesn't%20believe%20in%2C%20and%20won't%20settle%20for%20lowball%20fees%20%E2%80%94%20and%20says%20she%20was%20initially%20surprised%20when%20they%20were%20willing%20to%20match%20her%20understandable%20high%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20need%20the%20free%20makeup%2C%20and%20I%20didn't%20need%20the%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20Frankel%2C%20who%20maintained%20ownership%20of%20the%20Skinnygirl%20brand%20of%20food%20and%20lifestyle%20products%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20make%20millions%20of%20dollars%20on%20popcorn%20and%20dressing%20and%20shapewear%20while%20I%20sleep.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224288%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Frankel%20doesn't%20have%20grand%20plans%20for%20her%20beauty%20line%20but%20keeps%20her%20options%20open.%20Next%20up%3F%20An%20acting%20gig.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d0039cf533b039a884f299%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222734%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFrankel%20doesn't%20have%20grand%20plans%20for%20her%20beauty%20line%20but%20keeps%20her%20options%20open.%20Next%20up%3F%20An%20acting%20gig.%3Cp%3EPhoto%20by%20Heidi%20Gutman%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%3EFrankel's%20path%20from%20reality%20TV%20to%20Skinnygirl%20to%20acting%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20unfamiliar%2C%20Frankel%20wasn't%20just%20in%20reality%20TV%20%E2%80%94%20she%20made%20Housewives%20history%20when%20she%20founded%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fskinnygirl-cocktails-is-the-fastest-growing-spirits-brand-2012-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESkinnygirl%20Cocktails%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20then%20sold%20it%20in%202011.%20The%20actual%20acquisition%20price%20of%20Skinnygirl%20is%20up%20for%20debate%3A%20It%20was%20reported%20to%20be%20as%20much%20as%20%24120%20million%2C%20but%20both%20the%20company%20and%20Frankel%20haven't%20disclosed%20the%20final%20amount%2C%20which%20included%20contingency%20payouts%20based%20on%20sales%20goals%2C%20according%20to%20SEC%20filings.%20The%20deal%20was%20big%20enough%20to%20prompt%20networks%20to%20include%20so-called%20%26quot%3BBethenny%20Clauses%26quot%3B%20in%20reality%20TV%20contracts%2C%20which%20require%20reality%20stars%20to%20give%20the%20networks%20a%20cut%20of%20businesses%20promoted%20on%20air.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20any%20influencer%2C%20Frankel%20says%20she's%20completely%20honest%20about%20what%20she%20likes%20and%20doesn't.%20What's%20different%20is%20there's%20a%20%3Cem%3Elot%3C%2Fem%3E%20she%20doesn't%20seem%20to%20like%2C%20which%20in%20turn%20makes%20her%20positive%20reviews%20and%20opinions%20even%20more%20valuable.%20Fewer%20than%201%25%20of%20her%20posts%20are%20sponsored%2C%20one%20of%20her%20representatives%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20left%20reality%20TV%20and%20honestly%20thought%20the%20faucet%20would%20turn%20off%20because%20that's%20what%20happens%2C%20and%20I%20was%20fine%20with%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20can't%20be%20bought.%20Brands%20maybe%20find%20it%20refreshing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20her%20entrepreneurial%20history%2C%20she's%20not%20interested%20in%20starting%20her%20own%20beauty%20line%20%E2%80%94%20a%20route%20that%20many%20celebrities%20and%20influencers%2C%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flady-gagas-haus-labs-flopped-on-amazon-relaunching-sephora-2022-5%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIn%2520May%2520the%2520company%2520announced%2Cidentities%2520are%2520known%2520to%2520Insider.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ELady%20Gaga%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsephora-addison-raes-item-beauty-hyram-yarbros-selfless-dropping-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EAddison%20Rae%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20have%20tried%2C%20to%20varying%20degrees%20of%20success.%20She%20said%20she%20turned%20down%20a%20well-known%20dermatologist%20who%20wanted%20to%20partner%20up.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'd%20rather%20have%20someone%20else%20that's%20got%20the%20big%20research%20and%20development%20spend%20millions%20and%20billions%20of%20dollars%20on%20that%20and%20let%20them%20carry%20it%20on%20their%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BLet%20me%20just%20be%20the%20creative%20and%20the%20face%20and%20the%20messenger.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20what%20%3Cem%3Eis%3C%2Fem%3E%20next%3F%20At%20the%20moment%2C%20it's%20acting.%20When%20BI%20spoke%20with%20her%2C%20she%20was%20about%20to%20board%20a%20plane%20to%20a%20movie%20gig.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20tables%20go%20cold%2C%20I%20walk%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20tables%20go%20hot%2C%20I%20keep%20pressing%20my%20bets.%20You%20want%20to%20call%20me%3F%20You%20want%20to%20pay%20me%20six%20figures%20to%20do%20a%20movie%3F%20Sure.%20You%20want%20to%20call%20me%20to%20use%20my%20mascara%20that%20I%20talked%20about%20that%20I%20liked%3F%20Great.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20her%2C%20is%20reality%20over%20for%20good%3F%20Not%20necessarily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20can't%20pay%20me%20enough%2C%20is%20the%20problem%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20can't%20pay%20me%20enough%20money%20for%20me%20to%20leave%20this%20house%2C%20get%20hair%20and%20makeup%20on%2C%20go%20somewhere.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20not%20a%20problem%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20making%20a%20TikTok.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-bethenny-frankel-real-housewife-became-influencer-lucrative-business-earnings-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708167121000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cfd255a610a9069d5a2b59%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-bethenny-frankel-real-housewife-became-influencer-lucrative-business-earnings-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bethenny%20Frankel%20left%20reality%20TV.%20Now%2C%20she%20says%20she's%20making%20more%20annually%20as%20an%20influencer%20than%20a%20Real%20Housewife%2C%20and%20raked%20in%20%243.2%20million%20in%202023.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mberg%40businessinsider.com%20(Madeline%20Berg)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-bethenny-frankel-real-housewife-became-influencer-lucrative-business-earnings-2024-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%2C%20Canada%20Foreign%20Ministers%20Have%20First%20Publicised%20Meeting%20Since%20Nijjar%20Killing%20Accusation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17161843%2FScreenshot-2024-02-17-at-4.18.09.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20For%20only%20the%20second%20time%20since%20Canada%20levelled%20accusations%20against%20India%20regarding%20the%20killing%20of%20a%20Canadian%20citizen%2C%20the%20foreign%20ministers%20of%20the%20two%20countries%20met%20in%20Germany%20%E2%80%93%20for%20their%20first%20publicised%20meeting%20%E2%80%93%20to%20discuss%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20the%20first%20time%20that%20both%20Canada%20and%20India%20have%20publicised%20a%20meeting%20of%20their%20foreign%20ministers%20since%20September.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20two%20minister%20had%2C%20however%2C%20met%20in%20Washington%20shortly%20after%20the%20contentious%20allegations%20were%20aired%2C%20when%20the%20Indian%20foreign%20minister%20was%20in%20United%20States%20to%20attend%20the%20UN%20General%20Assembly.%20This%20meeting%20was%20unannounced%20and%20was%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findia-canada-jaishankar-melanie-joly-washington-meeting%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eneither%20officially%20denied%20nor%20confirmed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20either%20Ottawa%20or%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOver%20four%20months%20later%2C%20both%20countries%20announced%20their%20meeting%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20Munich%20Security%20Conference%20on%20Friday%2C%20February%2016.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COur%20conversation%20understandably%20focused%20on%20the%20present%20state%20of%20our%20bilateral%20ties.%20Was%20also%20useful%20to%20exchange%20views%20on%20the%20global%20situation%2C%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FDrSJaishankar%2Fstatus%2F1758602722528379278%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Indian%20external%20affairs%20minister%20Jaishankar%20posted%20on%20X%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimilarly%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fmelaniejoly%2Fstatus%2F1758668177163292804%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ECanadian%20foreign%20minister%20Melanie%20Joly%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20w%3C%2Fspan%3Erote%20on%20X%3Cspan%3E%20that%20they%20had%20a%20%E2%80%9Cfrank%20discussion%20on%20Canada-India%20relations%20and%20the%20current%20global%20issues%2C%20including%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20illegal%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Advancements%E2%80%99%20after%20tension%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20September%2019%2C%20Canadian%20Prime%20minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20stood%20in%20the%20House%20of%20Commons%20and%20announced%20that%20there%20were%20%E2%80%9Ccredible%20allegations%E2%80%9D%20of%20Indian%20government%20agents%20being%20involved%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20a%20Canadian%20national%2C%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%20whom%20New%20Delhi%20describes%20as%20a%20Khalistani%20terrorist.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20and%20Canada%20had%20each%20expelled%20a%20senior%20diplomat%2C%20but%20New%20Delhi%20went%20further%20to%20stop%20visa%20services%20for%20Canadian%20nationals.%20India%20also%20forced%20Canada%20to%20downsize%20its%20diplomatic%20presence%20by%20calling%20for%20reciprocity%20in%20the%20size%20of%20embassies%20and%20other%20outposts%20in%20each%20other%E2%80%99s%20countries.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETwo%20months%20after%20Trudeau%E2%80%99s%20announcement%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fpannun-assassination-plot-india-enquiry-committee-set-up%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EUS%20prosecutors%20unsealed%20charges%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20against%20an%20Indian%20national%2C%20Nikhil%20Gupta%2C%20which%20linked%20an%20unnamed%20government%20official%20to%20the%20foiled%20attempt%20to%20murder%20a%20Khalistani%20group%E2%80%99s%20lawyer%20in%20New%20York%20by%20hiring%20a%20hitman.%20The%20November%20indictment%20also%20connected%20Nijjar%E2%80%99s%20killing%20in%20June%202023%20with%20the%20alleged%20conspiracy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20contrast%20to%20the%20reaction%20to%20Canada%2C%20India%20quickly%20set%20up%20a%20high-level%20committee%20to%20probe%20the%20allegations%20made%20by%20US%20investigators.%20However%2C%20no%20announcement%20about%20the%20result%20of%20the%20probe%20has%20been%20made%20so%20far.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELast%20month%2C%20the%20outgoing%20Canadian%20National%20Security%20Advisor%20Jody%20Thomas%20had%20claimed%20there%20was%20%E2%80%9Cadvancements%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20relationship.%20She%20had%20also%20said%20in%20her%20interview%20to%20Canadian%20media%20that%20India%20was%20%E2%80%9Ccooperating%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20investigation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20a%20week%20later%2C%20the%20Indian%20high%20commissioner%20to%20Canada%2C%20Sanjay%20Kumar%20Verma%20contradicted%20Thomas%20and%20said%20that%20New%20Delhi%20was%20not%20cooperating%20as%20it%20had%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fcanada-india-nsa-jody-thomas-sanjay-verma-nijjar%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eyet%20to%20receive%20any%20evidence%20from%20Canadian%20authorities%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20same%20day%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ourcommons.ca%2Fdocumentviewer%2Fen%2F44-1%2FFAAE%2Fmeeting-92%2Fevidence%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20Canadian%20House%20of%20Common%E2%80%99s%20standing%20committee%20on%20foreign%20affairs%20and%20international%20development%20held%20a%20hearing%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20where%20a%20senior%20Canadian%20diplomat%20noted%20that%20information%20from%20the%20police%20investigation%20had%20not%20yet%20been%20shared.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EConspiracy%20and%20inquiries%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWeldon%20Epp%2C%20the%20Canadian%20foreign%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20assistant%20deputy%20minister%20for%20the%20Indo-Pacific%2C%20told%20lawmakers%20that%20the%20Indian%20position%20has%20been%20that%20%E2%80%9Cuntil%20they%20receive%20evidence%20from%20a%20police%20investigation%2C%20they%20will%20reserve%20their%20right%20as%20to%20how%20they%20will%20respond%E2%80%9D.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CTherefore%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20inaccurate%20to%20say%20that%20while%20that%20investigation%20is%20still%20under%20way%2C%20the%20RCMP%20is%20not%20directly%20engaging%20the%20high%20commissioner%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20on%20February%205.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Royal%20Canadian%20Mounted%20Police%20(RCMP)%20is%20the%20primary%20investigative%20body%20for%20the%20case.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEarlier%2C%20Jaishankar%20had%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fone-has-provided-inputs-another-hasnt-jaishankar-on-indias-differing-responses-to-us-canada%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ejustified%20India%E2%80%99s%20differing%20reaction%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20US%20and%20Canada%20by%20arguing%20that%20only%20one%20of%20them%20has%20given%20%E2%80%9Cspecific%20evidence%20or%20inputs%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20senior%20Canadian%20foreign%20ministry%20official%20said%20that%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20Canadian%20and%20American%20inquiries%20were%20different%20as%20one%20was%20a%20murder%2C%20while%20another%20was%20a%20conspiracy%20to%20hire%20a%20hitman.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFurther%2C%20he%20pointed%20out%20the%20legal%20processes%20in%20US%20and%20Canada%20were%20very%20different.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20possibility%20for%20an%20early%20narrative%20and%20the%20disclosure%20of%20evidence%20through%20an%20indictment%20in%20the%20U.S.%20differs%20quite%20significantly%20from%20the%20legal%20process%20in%20Canada%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Epp.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20claimed%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cinflection%20point%20in%20a%20Canadian%20investigation%2C%20such%20that%20detailed%20information%20supporting%20the%20investigation%20can%20be%20released%20to%20the%20public%20or%20a%20foreign%20government%2C%20comes%20at%20a%20later%20stage%E2%80%9D.%20He%20added%20that%20due%20to%20the%20disclosure%20of%20the%20US%20indictment%20there%20was%20%E2%80%9Ca%20clear%20link%20being%20described%20by%20the%20evidence%20provided%20to%20date%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Asking%20questions%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDescribing%20the%20India%20setting%20up%20the%20%E2%80%9Cindependent%20high-level%20committee%E2%80%9D%20in%20response%20to%20US%20claims%20as%20a%20positive%20step%2C%20Epp%20observed%20that%20when%20investigation%20reaches%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccomparable%20inflection%20point%E2%80%9D%20in%20Canada%2C%20%E2%80%9Cmore%20information%20will%20be%20available%20for%20the%20Indian%20government%20and%20its%20high-level%20committee%20to%20consider%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Canadian%20diplomat%20also%20told%20lawmakers%20that%20Ottawa%20was%20in%20%E2%80%9Cintensive%E2%80%9D%20conversations%20with%20%E2%80%9Clike-minded%E2%80%9D%20allies%2C%20like%20United%20States%20and%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20over%20this%20ongoing%20challenge.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20three%20countries%2C%20the%20two%20partners%20you%20named%20and%20Canada%2C%20have%20large%20diaspora%20communities%20that%20have%20been%20targets%20of%20transnational%20crime.%20There%20have%20been%20challenges%20that%20affect%20these%20communities.%20There%E2%80%99s%20a%20concern%20for%20domestic%20security%20as%20well%20as%20for%20engaging%20India%20on%20addressing%20those%20domestic%20matters%20that%20may%20play%20out%20differently%20in%20our%20legal%20systems%20than%20they%20do%20in%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Epp%20as%20per%20the%20transcript.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20indicated%20that%20Ottawa%20had%20worked%20with%20the%20two%20countries%20to%20%E2%80%9Cask%20questions%20of%20our%20Indian%20colleagues%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20important%20to%20raise%20these%20questions%2C%20for%20Canada%20to%20raise%20them%2C%20to%20receive%20an%20official%20position%20from%20the%20Indian%20government%20and%20to%20hear%20from%20the%20Indian%20government%2C%20including%20from%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%2C%20that%20they%20will%2C%20%E2%80%9Cdefinitely%20look%20into%E2%80%9D%20any%20evidence%20and%20hold%20people%20accountable%20if%20there%E2%80%99s%20evidence%20provided.%20Working%20with%20our%20partners%2C%20we%E2%80%99ll%20have%20to%20continue%20to%20raise%20these%20issues%20and%20have%20those%20conversations%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Epp.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20issue%20of%20Indian%20government%E2%80%99s%20claims%20about%20activities%20of%20Khalistani%20groups%20in%20those%20three%20countries%20was%20also%20part%20of%20these%20conversations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6it%20is%20true%20that%20there%20have%20been%20discussions%2C%20both%20between%20our%20partners%20and%20India%20but%20also%20between%20our%20partners%E2%80%94between%20us%2C%20the%20U.K.%20and%20the%20U.S.%E2%80%94because%20we%20are%20all%20dealing%20with%20some%20similar%20impacts%20of%20differences%20between%20our%20legal%20systems%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20just%20say%2C%20and%20that%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%2C%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20how%20to%20deal%20with%20allegations%20of%20terrorism%20and%20extremism%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESensationalising%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20had%20also%20complained%20publicly%20that%20Canada%20had%20gone%20public%20over%20its%20allegations%20despite%20New%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20request%20for%20sharing%20information.%20While%20Trudeau%20had%20raised%20the%20matter%20directly%20with%20his%20Indian%20counterpart%20during%20the%20G-20%20summit%2C%20other%20senior%20Canadian%20officials%20had%20also%20visited%20New%20Delhi%20earlier.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20answer%20to%20repeated%20questions%20regarding%20Trudeau%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%2