%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Elose%20fat%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Megan%20said%20she%E2%80%99s%20in%20%E2%80%9Ca%20slump%E2%80%9D%20exercise-wise%20and%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20worked%20out%20properly%20for%20over%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20get%20minimal%20exercise%20daily%2C%E2%80%9D%20Megan%20said.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20I%20am%20trying%20to%20go%20for%20a%2020-minute%20walk%20every%20morning%20and%20night.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDietitian%20Alix%20Turoff%20told%20BI%20that%2040%20minutes%20of%20walking%20every%20day%20is%20a%20great%20start.%20%E2%80%9COnce%20Megan%20gets%20into%20a%20consistent%20routine%20with%20walking%2C%20I%20would%20encourage%20her%20to%20start%20incorporating%20strength%20training%20exercises%20into%20her%20routine%20to%20help%20her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-exercises-for-building-muscle-in-gym-correct-technique-2020-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ebuild%20muscle%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%20%E2%80%9CSince%20she%20is%20not%20currently%20following%20a%20regular%20strength%20training%20routine%2C%20she%20could%20start%20with%20bodyweight%20exercises%20or%20light%20weights.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EEat%20fruit%20and%20vegetables%20at%20breakfast%20to%20get%20more%20fiber%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20typical%20day%2C%20Megan%20has%20an%20egg%20and%20goats%20cheese%20omelet%20for%20breakfast%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMegan%20is%20doing%20a%20good%20job%20of%20having%20protein%20at%20each%20meal%2C%20Turoff%20said.%20However%2C%20she%20would%20benefit%20from%20adding%20more%20color%20to%20her%20diet%20in%20the%20form%20of%20fruits%20and%20vegetables.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIncorporating%20more%20produce%20can%20significantly%20increase%20your%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnutrition-for-weight-loss-principles-eat-fiber-protein-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Efiber%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20intake%20which%20is%20essential