k%20and%20stunning.%20%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESoft%2C%20warm%20lights%20enveloped%20the%20vast%20and%20immaculate%20space%20as%20dozens%20of%20gold%20bow%20ties%20playfully%20glowed%20behind%20the%20check-in%20desk.%20Transparent%20beams%20that%20stretched%20from%20the%20pristine%20marble%20floors%20to%20the%20soaring%20ceiling%20felt%20reminiscent%20of%20Singapore's%20famous%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsingapore-supertrees-gardens-by-the-bay-crazy-rich-asians-2018-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESupertree%20Grove%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20space%20felt%20modern%20and%20tranquil%2C%20already%20promising%20a%20very%20different%20kind%20of%20oasis%20in%20Sin%20City.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAt%20the%20center%20was%20a%20stunning%20display%20of%20fresh%20roses%20and%20orchids.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Fontainebleau%20lobby%20flowers%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cd1028f533b039a883ae0c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBeautiful%20flowers%20greeted%20me%20at%20the%20center%20of%20the%20lobby.%20%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20counted%20nine%20large%20vases%20of%20flowers%2C%20and%20a%20friendly%20greeter%20I%20spoke%20with%20estimated%20there%20were%20about%20100%20stems%20in%20each.%20She%20said%20the%20flowers%20were%20changed%20every%20three%20days%20and%20switched%20out%20depending%20on%20the%20holiday%20season.%20The%20red%20roses%20were%20celebrating%20Valentine's%20Day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20the%20women%20love%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20with%20a%20smile.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlmost%20as%20if%20on%20cue%2C%20a%20young%20girl%20sprinted%20toward%20the%20flowers%20to%20see%20if%20they%20were%20real.%20It%20was%20exactly%20what%20I%20had%20done%20mere%20moments%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ETucked%20away%20next%20to%20the%20check-in%20desk%20is%20the%20exclusive%205%2C000-square-foot%20VIP%20lounge.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Fontainebleau%20VIP%20room%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cd105394aa8ee8e84b639d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221229%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20VIP%20entrance%20at%20the%20Fontainebleau.%20%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMetallic%20gold%20doors%20beckon%20into%20the%20luxury%20lounge%2C%20where%20guests%20of%20the%20Fontainebleau's%20Fleur%20de%20Lis%20suites%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0which%20start%20at%20%245%2C000%20a%20night%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0begin%20their%20stay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20lounge%20features%20a%20private%20place%20to%20relax%20and%20grab%20complimentary%20drinks%20and%20pastries.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Fontainebleau%20VIP%20lounge%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cd106d6fcb546d2d4fd13c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221619%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20VIP%20lounge%20at%20Fontainebleau.%20%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAirport%20lounges%20should%20take%20note%20of%20the%20style%20achieved%20by%20Fontainebleau's%20VIP%20area.%20The%20deep-blue%20carpet%20and%20couches%20are%20luxe%20and%20sophisticated%2C%20and%20the%20gold%20mirrors%20and%20light%20fixtures%20%E2%80%94%20combined%20with%20marble%20detailing%20%E2%80%94%20look%20extremely%20elegant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20flute%20of%20crisp%20Champagne%20is%20offered%20to%20VIP%20guests%20on%20arrival%2C%20who%20can%20also%20grab%20fresh%20pastries%20or%20hot%20tea%20whenever%20they%20need.%20The%20lounge%20also%20provides%20a%20quick%20shortcut%20to%20the%20elevators%2C%20perfect%20for%20any%20famous%20guest%20who%20doesn't%20want%20to%20pass%20through%20the%20casino.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBut%20you%20don't%20need%20to%20be%20a%20VIP%20to%20enjoy%20the%20most%20beautiful%20parts%20of%20the%20Fontainebleau.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Fontainebleau%20casino%20area%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cd14106fcb546d2d4fd344%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFontainebleau's%20main%20floor%20is%20filled%20with%20fresh%20flowers%20and%20sleek%20architecture.%20%3Cp%3EDavid%20Becker%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20Fontainebleau%20Las%20Vegas%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20always%20believed%20that%20real%20luxury%20is%20in%20the%20small%20details%2C%20and%20the%20amount%20of%20thought%20that%20went%20into%20every%20inch%20of%20the%20hotel's%20interior%20is%20immensely%20impressive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESubtle%20bow%20ties%20paying%20homage%20to%20the%20Fontainebleau%20Miami%20are%20hidden%20across%20the%20resort.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Fontainebleau%20chandelier%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cd165df533b039a883b25b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20chandelier%20above%20Bleau%20Bar%20at%20the%20Fontainebleau%20Las%20Vegas.%20%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20late%20architect%20Morris%20Lapidus%2C%20who%20designed%20the%20original%20Fontainebleau%2C%20incorporated%20his%20signature%20bow%20tie%20into%20the%20design%20of%20the%20resort's%20interior.%20Now%2C%20it's%20the%20emblem%20of%20the%20Las%20Vegas%20edition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%201%2C200%20golden%20bow%20ties%20sparkling%20from%20the%2060-foot-tall%20centerpiece%20chandelier%20that%20hangs%20above%20the%20bar%20on%20the%20main%20floor%2C%20and%20miniature%20bow%20ties%20are%20hidden%20in%20a%20stylish%20pattern%20of%20circles%20that%20burst%20against%20the%20casino's%20navy%20carpet.%20There%20are%20tiny%20bow%20ties%20stitched%20into%20the%20back%20of%20plush%20periwinkle%20leather%20chairs%20beckoning%20you%20to%20each%20slot%20machine%2C%20while%20chrome%20bow%20ties%20gleam%20from%20the%20handles%20on%20every%20dresser%20in%20the%20suites.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20find%20the%20bow%20ties%20to%20be%20cartoonish%20or%20excessive%2C%20but%20rather%20sweet%20surprises%20I%20kept%20discovering%20throughout%20my%20two-night%20stay.%20Their%20subtle%20and%20sophisticated%20design%20paired%20well%20with%20the%20old-school%20Frank%20Sinatra%20rat-pack%20energy%20that%20exuded%20from%20the%20hotel's%20main%20bars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EEven%20the%20hotel's%20150%2C000-square-foot%20casino%20feels%20luxurious.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225934%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Casino%20at%20Fontainebleau%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cd139f94aa8ee8e84b6510%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%227912%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20casino%20at%20Fontainebleau%20Las%20Vegas%20features%201%2C300%20slot%20machines%2C%20plus%20card%20tables.%20%3Cp%3EGeorge%20Rose%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20hard%20to%20make%20slot%20machines%20(1%2C300%20to%20be%20exact)%20look%20sexy%2C%20but%20smart%20design%20touches%20help%20keep%20their%20presence%20from%20dominating%20the%20Fontainebleau's%20overall%20energy.%20Straight%20away%2C%20the%2042-foot%20ceiling%20makes%20the%20main%20floor%20of%20the%20resort%20feel%20big%20and%20grand.%20I%20really%20noticed%20its%20impact%20when%20I%20went%20into%20a%20different%20luxury%20hotel%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frob-gronkowski-super-bowl-party-las-vegas-photos-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Efor%20a%20Super%20Bowl%20party%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20instantly%20felt%20cramped.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Fontainebleau%20also%20helps%20keep%20the%20space%20serene%20by%20opting%20for%20muted%20blue%20carpets%2C%20soft%20blue%20lighting%2C%20and%20modern%20panels%20on%20the%20ceiling.%20Even%20the%20elevator%20shafts%20were%20covered%20in%20marble.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20there's%20no%20usual%20ringing%20and%20pinging%20from%20the%20various%20machines.%20I%20immediately%20clocked%20that%20their%20sound%20was%20off%2C%20allowing%20Sinatra's%20lilting%20croon%20to%20fill%20the%20room%20instead.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAfter%20taking%20a%20tour%20of%20the%20hotel's%20main%20area%2C%20it%20was%20time%20to%20check%20out%20our%20room.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222858%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Fontainebleau%20gold%20king%20room%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cfb78fa610a9069d5a0ff1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222130%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Gold%20King%20room%20at%20Fontainebleau%20Las%20Vegas%20starts%20at%20%24300%20a%20night.%20%3Cp%3EPeter%20Arnell%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20my%20main%20gripes%20with%20many%20hotels%20is%20that%20they're%20either%20extremely%20bland%20or%20look%20like%20something%20out%20of%20a%20corporate%20office%2C%C2%A0even%20with%20a%20resort%20price%20tag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Gold%20King%20room%2C%20which%20starts%20at%20%24300%20a%20night%2C%20is%20thoughtfully%20designed%20in%20calming%20blues%20that%20felt%20fitting%20for%20a%20Miami-born%20resort.%20I%20loved%20the%20sky-blue%20textured%20wallpaper%20and%20navy%20headboard%20that%20framed%20our%20plush%20king%20bed%2C%20which%20was%20outfitted%20with%20super-soft%20500-thread-count%20cotton%20sheets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGold%20chrome%20nightstands%20and%20a%20coral-pink%20bench%20and%20chairs%20added%20pops%20of%20color%20that%20kept%20the%20space%20feeling%20modern%20and%20fresh.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20adored%20the%20room's%20luxe%20and%20stylish%20details%20%E2%80%A6%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gold%20king%20room%20at%20Fontainebleau%20Las%20Vegas%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cd1afb94aa8ee8e84b6a1f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20bed%20in%20the%20Gold%20King%20room%20was%20extremely%20plush%20and%20comfortable.%20%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20a%20perfect%20view%20of%20the%20Sphere%20and%20High%20Roller%20wheel%20from%20our%20window%2C%20which%20flooded%20the%20room%20with%20natural%20light%20when%20we%20clicked%20on%20the%20automatic%20drapes.%20I%20could%20also%20spot%20Fontainebleau's%20six-and-a-half%20acre%20pool%20deck%2C%20which%20will%20open%20when%20Las%20Vegas'%20dayclub%20season%20kicks%20off%20in%20March.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20room's%20overall%20atmosphere%20was%20coastal%20but%20stylish%2C%20a%20much-needed%20reprieve%20from%20the%20bright%20neon%20colors%20that%20tend%20to%20dominate%20Vegas%20hotels%20(look%20no%20further%20than%20the%20purple%20and%20red%20butterfly%20carpet%20that%20dominates%20Encore).%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E...%20and%20the%20incredible%20shower.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bathroom%20in%20Fontainebleau%20room%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cd17cc94aa8ee8e84b680d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221641%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20loved%20the%20shower%20at%20Fontainebleau%20Las%20Vegas.%20%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20great%20hotel%20shower%20is%20extremely%20important%20to%20me.%20What%20good%20is%20a%20perfect%20night's%20sleep%20if%20the%20morning%20starts%20with%20tepid%20temperatures%20and%20terrible%20water%20pressure%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%20such%20danger%20with%20the%20spa-like%20shower%20in%20our%20room%2C%20which%20ran%20the%20entire%20length%20of%20one%20of%20the%20bathroom's%20walls.%20The%20white%20mosaic%20tile%20glowed%20invitingly%2C%20and%20the%20ability%20to%20step%20right%20in%20without%20having%20to%20struggle%20with%20a%20jammed%20door%20or%20fumble%20over%20a%20high%20tub%20made%20it%20feel%20extra%20lush.%20The%20custom-made%20shampoo%2C%20conditioner%2C%20and%20body%20wash%20all%20smelled%20delicious%20and%20left%20my%20hair%20looking%20fantastic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWe%20were%20starving%20after%20an%20early-morning%20flight%2C%20so%20we%20hit%20up%20the%20Promenade%20%E2%80%94%20Fontainebleau's%20luxury%20food%20hall%20%E2%80%94%20for%20lunch.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221836%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Fontainebleau%20food%20court%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cd16c094aa8ee8e84b6739%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221398%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Promenade%20offered%20really%20delicious%20casual%20dining%20options.%20%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20am%20no%20stranger%20to%20a%20Las%20Vegas%20hotel%20food%20court.%20It's%20where%20the%20bulk%20of%20my%20dining%20occurred%20when%20I%20was%20a%2020-something%20trying%20to%20grab%20sustenance%20in%20the%20short%20period%20between%20the%20end%20of%20a%20pool%20party%20and%20the%20beginning%20of%20a%20nightclub.%20Meals%20were%20quick%2C%20fast%2C%20and%20usually%20in%20a%20brown%20McDonald's%20paper%20bag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Promenade%20offers%20fast%20and%20affordable%20dining%20options%20without%20yielding%20quality.%20Miami%20Slice%20and%20El%20Bagel%20pay%20homage%20to%20the%20resort's%20Florida%20roots%2C%20while%20Bar%20Ito%20offers%20hand%20rolls%20by%20Michelin-starred%20chefs%20Kevin%20Kim%20and%20Masa%20Ito.%20There's%20also%20an%20eponymous%20burger%20concept%20from%20celebrity%20chef%20Josh%20Capon%2C%20plus%20spots%20to%20grab%20fresh%20coffee%2C%20sandwiches%2C%20and%20tacos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20Promenade%20became%20one%20of%20my%20favorite%20places%20to%20eat%20throughout%20my%20stay.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pizza%20from%20Miami%20Slice%20at%20Fontainebleau%20Las%20Vegas%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cd16e3f533b039a883b2b1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Pepperoni%20Proper%20and%20La%20Salsera%20from%20Miami%20Slice.%20%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFull%20transparency%2C%20my%20boyfriend%20and%20I%20became%20pretty%20obsessed%20with%20the%20Promenade.%20We%20were%20first%20blown%20away%20by%20our%20lunch%20from%20Miami%20Slice%2C%20which%20we%20agreed%20featured%20some%20of%20the%20best%20pizza%20we've%20ever%20tasted.%20The%20Pepperoni%20Proper%C2%A0had%20a%20delicious%20crust%20that%20was%20light%2C%20crispy%2C%20and%20flaky%20all%20at%20once%2C%20while%20the%20La%20Salsera%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0a%20twist%20on%20vodka%20pizza%20with%20drizzles%20of%20pesto%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0instantly%20reminded%20me%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeghan-markle-pizza-place-new-york-city-rubirosa-taste-test-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERubirosa%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Manhattan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20did%20not%20expect%20to%20find%20one%20of%20the%20best%20pizzas%20of%20my%20life%20in%20Las%20Vegas%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20told%20Peter%2C%20who%20remarked%20that%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20top%20five%20pizzas%20I've%20had%2C%20period.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20went%20back%20to%20Miami%20Slice%20the%20next%20night%20and%20bumped%20into%20DJ%20John%20Summit%2C%C2%A0who%20has%20a%20residency%20at%20the%20Fontainebleau's%20club%20and%20told%20us%20how%20much%20he%20loves%20coming%20to%20eat%20at%20the%20Promenade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20tried%20El%20Bagel%2C%20Bar%20Ito%2C%20and%20Nona's%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0the%20sandwich%20spot%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20there%20wasn't%20a%20single%20dish%20that%20missed%20the%20mark.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ELater%20that%20day%2C%20I%20checked%20out%20the%20hotel's%2014%2C000-square-foot%20fitness%20center.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gym%20at%20Fontainebleau%20Las%20Vegas%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cd18576fcb546d2d4fd5f9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFontainebleau's%20huge%20gym%20was%20spotless.%20%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20worked%20out%20in%20some%20extremely%20depressing%20hotel%20gyms%2C%20even%20at%20very%20nice%20resorts.%20There%20are%20usually%20a%20few%20stray%20machines%2C%20bad%20fluorescent%20lighting%2C%20and%20a%20sad%20pile%20of%20weights%20in%20the%20corner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Fontainebleau's%20fitness%20center%2C%20which%20is%20flanked%20by%20an%20IV%20drip%20lounge%20and%20IGK%20salon%2C%20is%20sleek%20and%20state-of-the-art.%20Among%20the%20typical%20treadmills%20and%20StairMasters%20were%20Peloton%20bikes%2C%20VersaClimbers%2C%20and%20Hydrorowers%2C%20with%20a%20fresh%20rolled-up%20towel%20waiting%20in%20every%20cup%20holder.%20The%20weights%20section%20had%20every%20dumbbell%2C%20kettlebell%2C%20and%20barbell%20you%20could%20need%2C%20along%20with%20space%20for%20sled%20pushing%20or%20tire%20flipping.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20schedule%20at%20the%20front%20desk%20noted%20daily%20classes%20that%20were%20free%20for%20guests%2C%20including%20mat%20pilates%2C%20yoga%2C%20weight%20sculpting%2C%20and%20dance.%20Personal%20training%20sessions%20could%20also%20be%20purchased%20starting%20at%20%2475.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20was%20especially%20impressed%20by%20the%20huge%20recovery%20room.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221397%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Anneta%20at%20Fontainebleau%20Las%20Vegas%20gym%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cd1872f533b039a883b397%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221287%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEnjoying%20a%20service%20in%20the%20recovery%20room.%20%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20fairly%20certain%20the%20Fontainebleau's%20recovery%20room%20is%20bigger%20than%20my%20one-bedroom%20apartment%20in%20LA.%20The%20walls%20were%20lined%20with%20foam%20rollers%20and%20Theraguns%2C%20while%20different%20recovery%20stations%20offered%20treatments%20with%20acupressure%2C%20compression%2C%20and%20photon%20light.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20opted%20for%20a%2015-minute%20session%20with%20the%20compression%20leg%20sleeves%20(a%20%2435%20upgrade)%2C%20and%20a%20staff%20member%20helpfully%20explained%20how%20the%20boots%20would%20help%20speed%20up%20recovery%2C%20reduce%20soreness%2C%20and%20boost%20circulation%20and%20lymphatic%20drainage.%20After%20an%20hour%20of%20cardio%2C%20it%20was%20extremely%20relaxing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWe%20kicked%20off%20our%20first%20night%20in%20Las%20Vegas%20with%20a%20wild%20dinner%20at%20Papi%20Steak%2C%20which%20describes%20itself%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bultimate%20in%20a%20hedonistic%20night%20out.%26quot%3B%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227042%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Papi%20Steak%20at%20Fontainebleau%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cd13506fcb546d2d4fd2c7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224944%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPapi%20Steak%20is%20among%20the%2036%20restaurants%20offered%20at%20Fontainebleau.%20%3Cp%3EGeorge%20Rose%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPapi%20Steak%20at%20Fontainebleau%20Las%20Vegas%20is%20the%20second%20edition%20of%20the%20famous%20party%20restaurant%20helmed%20by%20Miami%20hospitality%20king%20David%20Grutman%20and%20David%20%26quot%3BPapi%26quot%3B%20Einhorn.%20I%20learned%20from%20our%20waiter%20that%20the%20restaurant's%20original%20concept%20was%20born%20after%20Grutman%20put%20Einhorn's%20signature%20steak%20on%20the%20menu%20of%20Komodo%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0another%20Miami%20restaurant%20with%20a%20location%20at%20Fontainebleau%20Las%20Vegas%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20it%20was%20an%20instant%20hit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey'd%20call%20Papi%20in%20when%20the%20Kardashians%20were%20there%20just%20to%20make%20steaks%20for%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20waiter%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20so%20Papi%20Steak%20was%20born%2C%20as%20was%20the%20showstopping%2055-ounce%20wagyu%20tomahawk%20that%20arrives%20tableside%20in%20a%20sparkling%20briefcase%C2%A0for%20diners%20who%20are%20happy%20to%20shell%20out%20%241%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20Papi%20Steak%20Beef%20Case%20moment%20is%20pure%20over-the-top%20Vegas.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Papi%20Steak%20at%20Fontainebleau%20Las%20Vegas%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cd188d94aa8ee8e84b688f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Papi%20Steak%20Beef%20Case%20costs%20%241%2C000.%20%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20saw%2015%20different%20Beef%20Case%20presentations%20during%20our%20two-hour%20dinner%2C%20each%20accompanied%20by%20flashing%20strobe%20lights%2C%20whoops%20and%20hollers%20from%20every%20waiter%2C%20and%20a%20cloud%20of%20smoke%20that%20billowed%20from%20above%20their%20heads%20as%20the%20%241%2C000%20steaks%20were%20branded.%20One%20woman%20waved%20her%20napkin%20in%20the%20air%20and%20danced%20along%20like%20it%20was%20a%20Greek%20wedding.%20Two%20guys%20ran%20over%20to%20take%20a%20thumbs-up%20selfie%20with%20the%20mighty%20tomahawk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Beef%20Case%20is%20the%20restaurant's%20showcase%2C%20but%20I%20was%20also%20delightfully%20surprised%20that%20every%20dish%20we%20tried%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0including%20the%20%2424%20Caesar%20salad%20and%20%2418%20latkes%20%E2%80%94%20was%20truly%20delicious.%20I've%20been%20to%20plenty%20of%20celebrity%20restaurants%20that%20coast%20on%20the%20clout%20of%20Instagram%20clicks%20and%20crazy%20menu%20items%2C%20but%20Papi%20Steak's%20food%20makes%20for%20a%20memorable%20night%20even%20if%20you%20don't%20shell%20out%20for%20its%20signature%20dish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAnd%20a%20nightcap%20at%20Nowhere%20was%20one%20of%20my%20favorite%20memories%20from%20the%20trip.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nowhere%20bar%20at%20Fontainebleau%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cd12f0f533b039a883af74%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENowhere%20was%20one%20of%20my%20favorite%20spots%20at%20Fontainebleau.%20%3Cp%3EDenise%20Truscello%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20Fontainebleau%20Las%20Vegas%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENowhere%20was%20next%20to%20the%20elevator%20that%20whizzed%20us%20up%20to%20our%20suite%2C%20and%20my%20boyfriend%20and%20I%20couldn't%20resist%20popping%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInspired%20by%20the%20late%20fashion%20designer%20Yves%20Saint%20Laurent's%20Parisian%20apartment%2C%20Nowhere%20exudes%20the%20kind%20of%20easy%20luxury%20and%20class%20that%20so%20many%20modern%20speakeasies%20search%20for%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0but%20few%20achieve.%20The%20walls%2C%20covered%20in%20varying%20shades%20of%20cream%2C%20glowed%20under%20the%20warm%20lighting%20as%20dark%20cabernet%20curtains%20framed%20the%20stage%20where%20a%20woman%20in%20a%20bright-red%20dress%20sang%20with%20a%20full%20band%20behind%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20sipped%20our%20delicious%20drinks%2C%20I%20watched%20a%20couple%20joyfully%20spin%20to%20the%20jazz%20music.%20The%20woman%20was%20dressed%20head%20to%20toe%20in%20a%20turquoise%20outfit%20with%20a%20matching%20pillbox%20hat.%20It%20felt%20like%20we'd%20been%20transported%20to%20a%20different%20era.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAfter%20a%20great%20night's%20sleep%2C%20I%20began%20my%20day%20at%20the%20Fontainebleau's%2055%2C000-square-foot%20spa.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lapis%20Spa%20at%20Fontainebleau%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cd1a43f533b039a883b4ca%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20starry%20night%20napping%20room%20at%20Fontainebleau.%20%3Cp%3EMark%20Medina%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20been%20to%20some%20gorgeous%20spas%20before%20(the%20hydrotherapy%20room%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpablo-escobar-former-mansion-resort-tulum-photos-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECasa%20Malca%20in%20Tulum%3C%2Fa%3E%20remains%20a%20favorite)%2C%20but%20I%20haven't%20experienced%20anything%20quite%20like%20Lapis%20at%20the%20Fontainebleau.%20The%20two-story%20spa%20features%20everything%20from%20an%20infrared%20sauna%20and%20steam%20room%20to%20a%20purifying%20salt%20cave%20and%20shower%20that%20rinses%20you%20off%20with%20falling%20snow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20relaxing%20morning%20began%20with%20the%2045-minute%20%26quot%3BReboot%20Signature%20Massage.%26quot%3B%20I%20then%20went%20into%20the%20coed%20sensory%20room%2C%20which%20glows%20with%20mellow%20lights%20designed%20to%20mimic%20the%20body's%20circadian%20rhythms%2C%20and%20hit%20the%20sauna%20before%20taking%20a%20refreshing%20dip%20in%20the%20cold%20plunge%20pool.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20unwinding%20in%20the%20hot%20tub%2C%20I%20cleared%20my%20senses%20(and%20sinuses)%20in%20the%20herbal%20inhalation%20room%20and%20relaxed%20on%20one%20of%20the%20heated%20stone%20loungers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBefore%20hitting%20up%20a%20celebrity-packed%20Komodo%20for%20dinner%20that%20night%2C%20I%20got%20a%20sneak%20peek%20at%20its%20legendary%20Peking%20duck.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Peking%20Duck%20at%20Komodo%20in%20Fontainebleau%20Las%20Vegas%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cd18d66fcb546d2d4fd62c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Peking%20duck%20at%20Komodo.%20%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20window%20next%20to%20the%20entrance%20of%20Komodo%20offers%20a%20glimpse%20into%20its%20duck%20room%2C%20where%20I%20got%20to%20watch%20as%20the%20%24115%20dish%20was%20prepared%20from%20start%20to%20finish.%20The%20glistening%20crispy%20duck%20%E2%80%94%20eaten%20inside%20a%20delicate%20pancake%20topped%20with%20cucumber%2C%20scallions%2C%20and%20a%20hoisin-like%20sauce%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0was%20deliciously%20rich%20and%20tender.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20could%20see%20why%20Komodo%20was%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20hot%20spots%20of%20the%20weekend%2C%20attracting%20the%20likes%20of%20Shaquille%20O'Neal%20(who%20dined%20a%20few%20feet%20away%20from%20us%20before%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsuper-bowl-parties-in-las-vegas-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehis%20Super%20Bowl%20party%3C%2Fa%3E)%2C%20Tom%20Brady%2C%20Kevin%20Durant%2C%20and%20Alicia%20Keys.%20Mark%20Wahlberg%20even%20went%20behind%20the%20bar%20to%20serve%20some%20cocktails%20for%20guests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWe%20danced%20the%20night%20away%20at%20LIV%2C%20the%20Fontainebleau's%20brand-new%20club.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Anneta%20at%20LIV%20nightclub%20at%20Fontainebleau%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cd19ac6fcb546d2d4fd6b0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMe%20in%20front%20of%20the%20sign%20at%20LIV.%20%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELIV%20has%20already%20made%20itself%20competitive%20in%20Las%20Vegas'%20stacked%20clubbing%20scene%20by%20scoring%20residencies%20with%20Calvin%20Harris%20and%20Tiesto%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0two%20of%20the%20world's%20biggest%20DJs%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0as%20well%20as%20John%20Summit%2C%20who's%20currently%20headlining%20the%20biggest%20electronic%20music%20festivals.%20We%20caught%20Summit's%20set%20during%20the%20club's%20Super%20Bowl%20weekend%20kickoff%20and%20were%20impressed%20by%20everything%20LIV%20had%20to%20offer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20at%2050%2C000%20square%20feet%2C%20LIV%20feels%20more%20intimate%20than%20some%20of%20the%20other%20big%20Vegas%20clubs%20and%20offers%20much%20better%20views%20and%20proximity%20to%20the%20stage.%20The%20sound%20quality%20was%20excellent%2C%20as%20reviewed%20by%20my%20DJ%20boyfriend%2C%20and%20the%20back%20bar%20behind%20the%20DJ%20booth%20made%20it%20surprisingly%20quick%20and%20easy%20to%20get%20drinks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBefore%20our%20Vegas%20trip%20ended%2C%20I%20had%20one%20last%20phenomenal%20meal%20at%20KYU.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22KYU%20restaurant%20in%20Fontainebleau%20Las%20Vegas%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cd18fb94aa8ee8e84b68cb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20interior%20of%20KYU%20at%20Fontainebleau%20Las%20Vegas.%20%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20got%20to%20go%20behind%20the%20scenes%20at%20KYU%20and%20watch%20as%20Chef%20Christopher%20Arellanes%20prepared%20his%20signature%20dish%2C%20the%20%24265%20royal%20golden%20chicken.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArellanes%20told%20me%20he%20wanted%20to%20give%20KYU%20a%20showstopping%20dish%20with%20a%20fine-dining%20twist%2C%20and%20he's%20truly%20achieved%20it.%20The%20melt-in-your-mouth%20royal%20golden%20chicken%20%E