s%20another%20plus%20that%20has%20helped%20me%20professionally%2C%20allowing%20me%20to%20build%20my%20freelance%20clientele.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAside%20from%20the%20diversity%2C%20the%20quality%20of%20living%20is%20significantly%20better%C2%A0in%20California%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Bay%20Area%20and%20San%20Diego%2C%20I%20really%20like%20that%20I%20can%20just%20pack%20up%20and%20drive%2020%20minutes%20to%20the%20beach%20or%20go%20to%20an%20art%20show.%20The%20amount%20of%20entertainment%20is%20greater.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20really%20love%20how%20much%20more%20involved%20Californians%20are%20with%20local%20politics.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fncoc.org%2Fresearch-type%2F2023-arkansas-civic-health-index%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELack%20of%20interest%20in%20state%20politics%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20a%20huge%20issue%20in%20my%20home%20state%2C%20leaving%20people%20uninformed.%20I%20feel%20most%20Californians%20are%20more%20educated%20and%20aware%20of%20politics%20on%20a%20state%20level%20and%20are%20actively%20involved%20in%20improving%20circumstances%20within%20their%20communities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20when%20I%20moved%20to%20California%2C%20I%20found%20a%20lot%20of%20resources%20for%20children%20with%20autism.%20My%20son%20has%20autism%20and%20has%20an%20individualized%20education%20plan%20here.%20I've%20found%20that%20the%20schools%20are%20always%20able%20to%20point%20us%20to%20additional%20community%20resources%20like%20regional%20centers%20and%20YMCAs.%20There%20are%20also%20resources%20for%20mental%20health%20support%2C%20neurodivergent%20folks%2C%20queer%20folks%2C%20and%20women%20of%20color.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20sure%20Arkansas%20also%20has%20these%20resources%2C%20but%20I%20love%20how%20much%20more%20accessible%20they%20are%20where%20I%20currently%20live.%20In%20Arkansas%2C%20many%20resources%20were%20concentrated%20in%20Little%20Rock.%20When%20I%20lived%20outside%20Little%20Rock%2C%20I%20remember%20d