%20to%20you%20and%20ask%20for%20your%20votes%20on%20emotional%20issues%20but%20it%20is%20up%20to%20you%20to%20decide%20whether%20you%20will%20vote%20on%20emotional%20grounds%20or%20to%20continue%20development%20work%20and%20for%20the%20welfare%20of%20your%20future%20generations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20the%20formation%20of%20Maharashtra%20state%20and%20the%20commencement%20of%20elections%20till%20date%2C%20it%20has%20never%20happened%20in%20Baramati%20that%20the%20deposit%20of%20opposition%20candidate%20was%20not%20forfeited.%20And%20I%20am%20proud%20of%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Pawar%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnReacting%20to%20the%20developments%2C%20Ms%20Sule%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bit's%20a%20democracy%2C%20everyone%20here%20has%20the%20right%20to%20contest%20elections%20and%20hence%20it's%20a%20fair%20thing%20to%20say.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NCP%20was%20split%20in%20July%20last%20year%20after%20Ajit%20Pawar%20along%20with%20eight%20other%20MLAs%20joined%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde-led%20Maharashtra%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20earlier%20this%20month%20ruled%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar%20faction%20would%20be%20recognised%20as%20the%20'real%20NCP'%2C%20thereby%20giving%20it%20control%20over%20the%20party%20name%20and%20symbol%20(a%20clock)%20weeks%20before%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20and%20polls%20to%20fill%20six%20to-be-vacant%20Rajya%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20played%20out%20like%20the%20Sena%20vs%20Sena%20fight%2C%20in%20which%20the%20faction%20led%20by%20Eknath%20Shinde%20(made%20Chief%20Minister%20after%20rebelling%20and%20allying%20with%20the%20BJP)%20was%20called%20the%20'real%20Sena'%2C%20leaving%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20racing%2C%20weeks%20before%20an%20election%2C%20to%20find%20a%20new%20identity%20for%20the%20party%20his%20father%20founded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708164480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fv138fs0o_ajit-pawar-supriya-sule-ani_625x300_17_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbuzz-over-ajit-pawars-wife-vs-supriya-sule-in-family-stronghold-5074145%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Pawar%20family%20in%20Maharashtra%20might%20be%20in%20a%20head-to-head%20contest%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20with%20speculation%20of%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20wife%20Sunetra's%20potential%20candidacy%20against%20his%20cousin%20Supriya%20Sule.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbuzz-over-ajit-pawars-wife-vs-supriya-sule-in-family-stronghold-5074145%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbuzz-over-ajit-pawars-wife-vs-supriya-sule-in-family-stronghold-5074145%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbuzz-over-ajit-pawars-wife-vs-supriya-sule-in-family-stronghold-5074145%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Google%20explains%20how%20it%20wants%20to%20use%20AI%20to%20improve%20digital%20security%20of%20users%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708164465000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107777704%2Cimgsize-1976963.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fgadgets-news%2Fgoogle-launches-ai-cyber-defense-initiative-to-improve-digital-security%2Farticleshow%2F107777604.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Google%20launches%20the%20AI%20Cyber%20Defense%20Initiative%20to%20address%20the%20Defender%E2%80%99s%20Dilemma%20in%20cybersecurity.%20It%20includes%20%242%20million%20research%20grants%2C%20strategic%20partnerships%2C%20and%20focuses%20on%20code%20verification%2C%20AI's%20potential%20in%20cyber%20offense%20and%20defense%2C%20and%20developing%20resilient%20language%20models.%20%E2%80%8BThe%20company%20believes%20that%20the%20need%20of%20the%20hour%20is%20need%20targeted%20investments%2C%20partnerships%20between%20industry%20and%20government%2C%20and%20effective%20regulatory%20approaches%20to%20empower%20organisations%20to%20maximise%20the%20value%20from%20AI%20while%20limiting%20utility%20to%20adversaries.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20TECH%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fgadgets-news%2Fgoogle-launches-ai-cyber-defense-initiative-to-improve-digital-security%2Farticleshow%2F107777604.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Telangana%3A%20Congress%2C%20BRS%20Sparring%20Over%20Irrigation%20Projects%20Set%20the%20Tone%20for%20Parliament%20Poll%20Campaign%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17152650%2FEffect-2024-02-17T152637.214.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHyderabad%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20blame%20game%20between%20the%20ruling%20Congress%20and%20the%20main%20Opposition%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samiti%20(BRS)%20over%20irrigation%20projects%20has%20rocked%20politics%20in%20Telangana%2C%20setting%20the%20tone%20for%20a%20high-pitch%20campaign%20rivalry%20for%20the%20upcoming%20parliament%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20focussed%20on%20major%20cracks%20from%20top%20to%20bottom%20in%20a%20couple%20of%20tall%20piers%20of%20a%20barrage%20of%20Kaleswaram%20lift%20irrigation%20project%20on%20river%20Godavari%20at%20Medigadda%20in%20Jaishankar%20Bhoopalpally%20district.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20BRS%20has%20highlighted%20that%20the%20ruling%20party%20has%20compromised%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20interests%20by%20agreeing%20to%20handover%20the%20Srisailam%20and%20Nagarjunasagar%20dams%2C%20common%20projects%20located%20in%20the%20territorial%20jurisdiction%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20Telangana%20respectively%20on%20Krishna%20river%2C%20to%20a%20river%20management%20board%20of%20the%20Central%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20had%20set%20up%20boards%20for%20both%20rivers%20to%20resolve%20river%20water%20disputes%20between%20Telangana%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20as%20a%20sequel%20to%20the%20implementation%20of%20a%20bifurcation%20law%20related%20to%20erstwhile%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20There%20are%20no%20major%20inter-state%20disputes%20on%20the%20Godavari%20warranting%20the%20intervention%20of%20its%20river%20board%20but%20the%20two%20states%20have%20frequently%20got%20into%20confrontation%20protesting%20against%20excess%20drawal%20of%20water%20by%20each%20state%20over%20and%20above%20their%20due%20share%20and%20construction%20of%20new%20outlets%2C%20mainly%20the%20Rayalaseema%20lift-irrigation%20project%20by%20AP%20which%20was%20later%20stayed%20by%20the%20National%20Green%20Tribunal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sparring%20between%20the%20two%20parties%20in%20the%20last%20few%20weeks%20escalated%20to%20the%20level%20of%20the%20Congress%20organising%20a%20site%20visit%20to%20Medigadda%20barrage%2C%20nearly%20250%20kms%20away%20from%20Hyderabad%2C%20by%20its%20MLAs%20and%20that%20of%20the%20All%20India%20Majlis-e-Ittehadul%20Muslimeen%20(AIMIM)%20and%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(CPI)%20on%20February%2013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BRS%20and%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20were%20also%20invited%20to%20make%20it%20an%20all-party%20delegation%20but%20they%20gave%20it%20a%20miss.%20Incidentally%2C%20the%20BRS%20organised%20a%20major%20public%20meeting%20on%20the%20same%20day%20at%20Nalgonda%20against%20injustice%20sought%20to%20be%20done%20by%20the%20Congress%20for%20the%20Krishna%20river%20basin%20districts%20of%20Mahbubnagar%2C%20Rangareddy%2C%20Nalgonda%20and%20Khammam%20by%20handing%20over%20the%20projects%20to%20the%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParty%20president%20and%20former%20chief%20minister%20K.%20Chandrasekhar%20Rao%20made%20his%20first%20public%20appearance%20on%20the%20occasion%20after%20the%20defeat%20of%20BRS%20in%20the%20November%2030%20elections%20to%20the%20state%20Assembly.%20He%20also%20did%20not%20show%20up%20in%20two%20Assembly%20sessions%20after%20the%20polls%20due%20to%20a%20fracture%20of%20his%20hip%20bone.%20He%20was%2C%20however%2C%20administered%20oath%20as%20an%20MLA%20and%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20by%20the%20Speaker%20G.%20Prasad%20Kumar%20in%20the%20latter%E2%80%99s%20chamber%20on%20one%20of%20the%20days%20when%20the%20Assembly%20was%20not%20in%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20large%20contingent%20of%20media%20corps%20which%20was%20taken%20to%20Medigadda%20by%20the%20Congress%20in%20buses%20was%20shown%20the%20vertical%20cracks%20in%20the%20piers%20and%20how%20one%20of%20them%20sank%20three%20feet%20down%20in%20the%20river%20bed.%20A%20power%20point%20presentation%20highlighting%20the%20colossal%20loss%20caused%20to%20public%20money%20was%20made%20to%20chief%20minister%20A.%20Revanth%20Reddy%20and%20a%20huge%20gathering%20by%20irrigation%20and%20vigilance%20officials%20of%20the%20state%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReddy%20threatened%20to%20initiate%20steps%20to%20recover%20money%20from%20wrongdoers%20under%20provisions%20of%20the%20Revenue%20Recovery%20Act.%20He%20regretted%20that%20Rs%2093%2C000%20crore%20was%20already%20spent%20on%20the%20project%20though%20the%20new%20irrigable%20area%20created%20was%20only%2098%2C570%20acres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20presentation%20of%20vigilance%20findings%20by%20its%20Director%20General%20Rajeev%20Ratan%20highlighted%20several%20deviations%20in%20project%20execution%2C%20cost%20escalation%20and%20violation%20of%20dam%20safety%20norms.%20He%20said%20major%20blocks%20in%20the%20barrage%20were%20constructed%20by%20a%20sub-contracting%20agency%20and%20not%20by%20L%20%26amp%3B%20T%20which%20was%20awarded%20the%20contract.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20similar%20PowerPoint%20presentation%20was%20also%20made%20by%20the%20Congress%20government%20in%20the%20Assembly%20a%20day%20ahead%20of%20the%20visit%20to%20Medigadda%20and%20on%20February%2017%20when%20a%20white%20paper%20on%20irrigation%20was%20released%20by%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReleasing%20the%20white%20paper%2C%20irrigation%20minister%20N.%20Uttam%20Kumar%20Reddy%20said%20yet%20another%20barrage%20of%20the%20project%20at%20Annaram%20village%20had%20also%20started%20leaking%20the%20previous%20day.%20The%20National%20Dam%20Safety%20Authority%20which%20was%20requested%20to%20inspect%20the%20barrage%20had%20agreed%20to%20depute%20a%20team%20in%20a%20couple%20of%20days%20but%20asked%20the%20government%20to%20immediately%20dewater%20the%20barrage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20request%20by%20BRS%20to%20be%20allowed%20to%20make%20its%20own%20powerpoint%20presentation%20on%20how%20it%20stalled%20handing%20over%20projects%20was%20turned%20down%20by%20the%20Speaker%20on%20the%20grounds%20that%20there%20was%20no%20such%20precedent.%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20presentations%20by%20Congress%20highlighted%20that%20the%20draft%20manual%20to%20hand%20over%20projects%20to%20the%20Krishna%20River%20Management%20Board%20(KRMB)%20was%20approved%20by%20the%20previous%20BRS%20government%20in%202015%2C%20a%20year%20after%20the%20formation%20of%20Telangana%20State.%20This%20was%20confirmed%20by%20a%20letter%20written%20by%20Smita%20Sabharwal%2C%20Secretary%2C%20Irrigation%2C%20in%20then%20chief%20minister%20Chandrasekhar%20Rao%E2%80%99s%20office%2C%20in%20December%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20irrigation%20minister%20also%20tabled%20in%20the%20Assembly%20a%2047-page%20note%20about%20a%20gazette%20notification%20issued%20by%20the%20Centre%20bringing%20under%20the%20fold%20of%20KRMB%20the%20irrigation%20projects%2C%20correspondence%20between%20the%20state%20and%20Central%20governments%20and%20minutes%20of%20an%20Apex%20Council%20meeting%20presided%20by%20Union%20Jal%20Shakti%20Minister%20Gajendra%20Singh%20Shekhawat%20and%20attended%20by%20Telangana%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20chief%20ministers%20Chandrasekhar%20Rao%20and%20Y.%20S.%20Jaganmohan%20Reddy%20respectively.%20It%20was%20after%20the%20Apex%20Council%20meeting%20that%20the%20Centre%20notified%20the%20gazette%20and%20asked%20Telangana%20and%20AP%20governments%20to%20deposit%20within%20sixty%20days%20Rs%20200%20crore%20each%20as%20seed%20money%20with%20the%20board%20for%20operation%20and%20maintenance%20of%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BRS%20government%2C%20therefore%2C%20made%20a%20provision%20of%20Rs%20200%20crore%20in%20the%20budget%20last%20year.%3Cbr%3E%5CnBRS%20MLA%20and%20fomer%20irrigation%20minister%20T.%20Harish%20Rao%20denied%20that%20the%20BRS%20government%20had%20ever%20agreed%20to%20hand%20over%20projects%20to%20the%20KRMB.%20In%20fact%2C%20he%20said%20the%20Jal%20Shakti%20Ministry%20had%20noted%20in%20the%20minutes%20of%20a%20KRMB%20meeting%20after%20the%20Congress%20government%20was%20sworn%20in%20on%20December%207%20that%20the%20state%20had%20agreed%20to%20the%20proposal.%20He%20claimed%20that%20the%20PowerPoint%20presentations%20were%20full%20of%20falsehood.%20The%20irrigation%20secretary%20in%20the%20Congress%20government%20Rahul%20Bojja%20said%20the%20minutes%20were%20not%20recorded%20correctly%20and%20demanded%20correction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F04204057%2Fkcr-harish.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F04204057%2Fkcr-harish.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F04204057%2Fkcr-harish-300x196.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F04204057%2Fkcr-harish-1024x670.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-425082%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22785%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EKCR%20with%20his%20nephew%20T.%20Harish%20Rao.%20Photo%3A%20Facebook%2FT.%20Harish%20Rao%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarish%20Rao%20also%20said%20the%20BRS%20government%20had%20always%20maintained%20that%20there%20was%20no%20question%20of%20giving%20up%20projects%20until%20the%20share%20of%20Telangana%20in%20Krishna%20was%20revised%20upwards.%20Against%20512%20tmc%20ft%20and%20299%20tmc%20ft%20of%20water%20allotted%20to%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20Telangana%20respectively%20in%2066%3A34%20ratio%20as%20per%20bifurcation%20law%2C%20the%20BRS%20government%20demanded%20reallocation%20of%20water%20in%2050%3A50%20ratio%20till%20the%20operation%20protocols%20of%20projects%20were%20fixed.%20Only%20if%20this%20was%20conceded%2C%20the%20government%20agreed%20to%20handover%20projects%20and%20thus%20made%20a%20budget%20allocation%20of%20Rs%20200%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERao%20said%20the%20BRS%20government%20had%20addressed%2027%20letters%20to%20the%20Centre%20with%20its%20demand.%3Cbr%3E%5CnHe%20recalled%20that%20the%20government%20had%20filed%20a%20case%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20praying%20for%20reallocation%20of%20Krishna%20water%20between%20four%20riparian%20States%20%E2%80%93%20Maharashtra%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20Telangana%20and%20AP%20%E2%80%93%20but%20it%20was%20withdrawn%20at%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20intervention%20when%20it%20committed%20to%20referring%20the%20matter%20to%20Krishna%20Water%20Disputes%20Tribunal%20headed%20by%20Justice%20Brijesh%20Kumar.%20The%20issue%20has%20since%20been%20referred%20to%20the%20tribunal%20a%20couple%20of%20months%20ago%20but%20the%20respective%20States%20are%20yet%20to%20submit%20their%20pleadings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20contentions%20of%20the%20two%20sides%20hanged%20fire%2C%20the%20Congress%20government%20passed%20a%20resolution%20in%20the%20Assembly%20refusing%20to%20hand%20over%20control%20of%20common%20projects%20to%20KRMB%20unless%2C%20among%20others%2C%20water%20sharing%20between%20the%20two%20States%20was%20finalised%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20catchment%20area%2C%20drought-prone%20area%2C%20basin%20population%20and%20cultivable%20area.%20The%20catchment%20of%20Krishna%20in%20Telangana%20is%2068%20per%20cent%20but%20both%20parties%20have%20agreed%20to%20a%2050%3A50%20share%20in%20the%20total%20allocation%20of%20811%20tmc%20ft%20before%20the%20separation%20of%20erstwhile%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20as%20a%20temporary%20measure%2C%20pending%20the%20final%20award%20of%20the%20tribunal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BRS%20welcomed%20the%20resolution%20and%20claimed%20it%20was%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20victory.%20The%20government%20moved%20the%20resolution%20hurriedly%20in%20view%20of%20the%20public%20meeting%20of%20BRS%20at%20Nalgonda.%20But%2C%20better%20late%20than%20never%2C%20said%20Harish%20Rao.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20public%20meeting%20of%20BRS%20and%20site%20visit%20by%20MLAs%20at%20Medigadda%2C%20the%20slanging%20match%20between%20Chief%20Minister%20Revanth%20Reddy%20and%20his%20predecessor%20Chandrasekhar%20Rao%20hogged%20the%20limelight.%20Speaking%20on%20the%20Medigadda%20fiasco%20for%20the%20first%20time%20since%20the%20incident%20on%20October%2021%2C%20Chandrasekhar%20Rao%20said%20Kaleswaram%20project%20was%20not%20merely%20about%20Medigadda%20barrage.%20It%20was%20about%20three%20barrages%2C%20200%20kms%20of%20tunnel%2C%201%2C500%20kms%20of%20canal%20network%2C%20nineteen%20electric%20sub-stations%20for%20pumping%20water%20and%20twenty%20reservoirs.%20He%20made%20light%20of%20sinking%20of%20piers%20at%20Medigadda%20saying%20it%20happened%20with%20some%20other%20projects%20in%20the%20past%20also.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20meanwhile%20asked%20the%20Engineer-in-Chief%20of%20irrigation%20C.%20Muralidhar%20who%20was%20on%20extension%20of%20service%20to%20tender%20his%20resignation.%20It%20gave%20marching%20orders%20to%20another%20E-n-C%20N.%20Venkateswarlu%20who%20was%20in-charge%20of%20the%20Kaleswaram%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20report%20of%20the%20Comptroller%20and%20Auditor%20General%20of%20India%20tabled%20in%20the%20Assembly%20said%20the%20government%20and%20a%20special%20purpose%20vehicle%20formed%20for%20the%20project%20will%20require%20Rs%201.41%20lakh%20crore%20in%20the%20next%20fourteen%20years%20fir%20debt%20servicing.%20The%20SPV%20had%20raised%20market%20loans%20of%20Rs%2087%2C000%20crore%20till%20March%20last%20year%20with%20guarantees%20by%20State%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AP%20government%20wrote%20a%20letter%20to%20KRMB%20agreeing%20to%20handover%20it%E2%80%99s%20control%20on%20the%20two%20projects%20subject%20to%20Telangana%20also%20showing%20the%20same%20gesture.%20However%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20on%20November%2030%2C%20poll%20day%20for%20Telangana%20Assembly%20elections%2C%20deployed%20it%E2%80%99s%20police%20force%20half%20way%20down%20the%20road%20overbridge%20on%20Nagarjunasagar%20dam%20to%20release%20water%20through%20the%20canal%20that%20serviced%20the%20State.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20developments%20in%20irrigation%20sector%20are%20likely%20to%20have%20a%20serious%20bearing%20on%20the%20coming%20Parliament%20elections%20as%20the%20Congress%20has%20targeted%20to%20win%2014%20out%20of%2017%20seats%20in%20the%20State%20and%20the%20BRS%20focussed%20on%20checking%20erosion%20of%20the%20party%20base%2C%20particularly%20the%20grassroots%20level%20elected%20representatives%20who%20are%20defecting%20to%20the%20Congress%20in%20a%20big%20way.%20The%20BRS%20representatives%20have%20moved%20no%20confidence%20motions%20against%20chairpersons%20of%20the%20same%20party%20and%20ensured%20change%20of%20guard%20after%20crossing%20over%20to%20Congress%20in%20several%20local%20bodies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sitting%20MP%20of%20BRS%20representing%20Peddapalli%2C%20N.%20Venkatesh%20has%20also%20joined%20the%20Congress%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20it%E2%80%99s%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20at%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708164377000%2C%22visual%22%