%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20players%20on%20Saturday%20wore%20black%20armbands%20as%20a%20mark%20of%20respect%20in%20the%20memory%20of%20former%20captain%20Dattajirao%20Gaekwad%20on%20the%20third%20day%20of%20the%20ongoing%20third%20Test%20against%20England%20in%20Rajkot%20on%20Saturday.%20Dattajirao%2C%20who%20played%2011%20Tests%20for%20India%20between%201951%20and%201962%2C%20died%20on%20February%2013%20after%20remaining%20hospitalised%20for%2012%20days.%20At%2095%2C%20he%20was%20India's%20oldest%20living%20Test%20cricketer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDattajirao%20was%20the%20father%20of%20former%20India%20batter%20and%20coach%20Aunshuman%20Gaekwad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTeam%20India%20will%20be%20wearing%20black%20arm%20bands%20in%20memory%20of%20Dattajirao%20Gaekwad%2C%20former%20India%20captain%20and%20India's%20oldest%20Test%20cricketer%20who%20passed%20away%20recently%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20BCCI%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20shortly%20before%20the%20third%20day's%20play%20got%20underway%20here%20at%20the%20Niranjan%20Shah%20Stadium.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20right-handed%20batter%2C%20who%20could%20bowl%20both%20medium%20pace%20and%20leg-break%2C%20Dattajirao%20was%20India's%20captain%20during%20the%201959%20tour%20of%20England.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20captain%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sunil%20Gavaskar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F40594-sunil-manohar-gavaskar-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESunil%20Gavaskar%3C%2Fa%3E%20mentioned%20that%20India%20could%20have%20worn%20the%20black%20armband%20right%20from%20the%20first%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBetter%20late%20than%20never...%20they%20should've%20done%20it%20on%20Day%201%20but%20better%20late%20than%20never%2C%26quot%3B%20Gavaskar%20said%20on%20commentary.%20%26quot%3BHe%20was%20captain%20of%20the%20Indian%20team%20in%20a%20five-match%20series.%20He%20captained%20four%20out%20of%20the%20five%20matches%20and%20the%20othe