%20Against%20Lions'%20Names%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17121846%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-16-at-10.43.15-PM.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJalpaiguri%20(Bengal)%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%20has%20moved%20the%20circuit%20bench%20of%20the%20Kolkata%20high%20court%20against%20the%20fact%20that%20one%20of%20two%20lions%20brought%20to%20the%20state%20from%20Tripura%20was%20named%20%E2%80%98Sita.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20lions%20were%20brought%20from%20Tripura%E2%80%99s%20Sepahijala%20%C2%A0Zoological%20Park%20to%20the%20Bengal%20Safari%20Park%20in%20Siliguri%20on%20February%2012.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20lions%20was%20named%20%E2%80%98Akbar%E2%80%99%20and%20the%20other%20%E2%80%98Sita%E2%80%99.%20Akbar%20is%20a%20seven-year-old%20and%20Sita%20is%20six.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hindutva%20group%20is%20now%20up%20in%20arms%20over%20the%20fact%20that%20Akbar%E2%80%99s%20companion%20is%20Sita.%20While%20Akbar%20is%20also%20the%20name%20of%20a%20Mughal%20emperor%2C%20Sita%20is%20a%20character%20in%20the%20epic%20%3Cem%3ERamayan%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20is%20revered%20as%20a%20Hindu%20deity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fwest-bengal%2Fappeal-to-mamata-banerjee-to-name-lion-lioness-that-reached-bengal-safari-park-on-february-12%2Fcid%2F2000549%5C%22%3Ereports%20had%20said%20that%20the%20forest%20authorities%20would%20be%20requesting%20chief%20minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20name%20the%20lions%2C%20it%20is%20not%20clear%20if%20she%20was%20indeed%20the%20one%20to%20name%20them%20Akbar%20and%20Sita.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%2016%2C%20the%20local%20chapter%20of%20the%20VHP%20moved%20the%20Jalpaiguri%20circuit%20bench%20against%20the%20state%20government%20with%20a%20petition%20over%20the%20naming%20and%20demanding%20that%20Sita%E2%80%99s%20name%20be%20changed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3