required%20under%20Citizenship%20Act%201955%20and%20rules%2Fregulations%20issued%20thereunder%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20leaving%20India%20was%20not%20her%20choice%20and%20that%20she%20was%20forced%20to%20by%20the%20government%20which%20had%20claimed%20that%20her%20articles%20were%20%26quot%3Bmalicious%26quot%3B%20and%20harming%20%26quot%3Bthe%20interests%20of%20the%20sovereignty%20and%20integrity%20of%20India%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20notice%20to%20Dougnac%20also%20figured%20in%20the%20delegation-level%20talks%20between%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20French%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%2C%20who%20was%20the%20chief%20guest%20for%20the%20Republic%20Day%20celebrations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20January%2026%2C%20Foreign%20Secretary%20Vinay%20Kwatra%2C%20in%20response%20to%20a%20question%2C%20had%20said%20that%20France%20did%20%26quot%3Bappreciate%26quot%3B%20India's%20%26quot%3Bframe%20of%20reference%26quot%3B%20to%20look%20at%20the%20case%20purely%20through%20a%20lens%20of%20compliance%20with%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20are%20free%20to%20do%20what%20they%20are%20accredited%20to%20do%20in%20a%20given%20space.%20But%20here%20I%20think%20the%20principal%20issue%20is%20whether%20the%20person%20is%20compliant%20with%20the%20rules%20and%20regulations%20of%20the%20state%20under%20which%20they%20come%2C%26quot%3B%20Kwatra%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708150320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fagl0k25o_vanessa-dougnac-x_625x300_26_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffrench-journalist-vanessa-dougnac-after-row-over-oci-card-5073058%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22French%20journalist%20Vanessa%20Dougnac%20on%20Saturday%20left%20India%20saying%20s