s%20To%20Counter%20Narratives%20Around%20Caste%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16183610%2Fimage-1841.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EBengaluru%3A%20%3C%2Fb%3EIn%20November%202023%2C%20Bihar%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fpolitics%2Fnews%2Fbihar-caste-based-census-out-extremely-backward-class-is-36-01-backward-class-2713-11696234333143.html%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ereleased%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20findings%20of%20its%20caste%20survey%2C%20revealing%20tentative%20but%20crucial%20data%20on%20various%20caste%20groups%20in%20the%20state%2C%20and%20exposing%20privileges%20and%20disadvantages%20faced%20by%20caste%20groups.%20There%20has%20been%20a%20demand%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FINCIndia%2Fstatus%2F1647885542556672000%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eopposition%20parties%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20conduct%20a%20nationwide%20caste%20census%20to%20collate%20caste%20data.%20Such%20an%20exercise%20was%20last%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiaspend.com%2Fcover-story%2Fcaste-data-reservations-category-obc-backward-class-770095%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Econducted%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%201931.%20Some%20states%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fandhra-pradesh%2Fandhra-pradesh-begins-caste-census-2856610%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EAndhra%20Pradesh%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fhyderabad%2Fcaste-census-cong-govt-to-bring-bill-in-telangana-budget-session%2Farticleshow%2F107222887.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ETelangana%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20decided%20to%20conduct%20state-level%20surveys.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EWe%20have%20a%20stereotype%20about%20caste%20based%20on%20the%20varna%20hierarchy%20%5Btraditional%20birth-based%20Hindu%20social%20order%5D%20that%20it%20is%20ancient%20and%20stable%2C%20and%20nothing%20changes.%20The%20reality%20of%20caste%20is%20different%20at%20the%20regional%20level%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20sociologist%20Surinder%20S.%20Jodhka.%20Caste%20is%20an%20important%20indicator%20of%20social%20exclusion%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EWhile%20the%20population%20census%2C%20which%20is%20now%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20old%20and%20delayed%20by%20nearly%20three%20years%2C%20collects%20data%20on%20Scheduled%20Castes%20(SCs)%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(STs)%2C%20caste-based%20enumeration%20must%20be%20done%20by%20state%20governments%20because%20%E2%80%9Ccaste%20formations%20are%20regional%20in%20character%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EJodhka%20is%20a%20professor%20of%20sociology%20at%20the%20Centre%20for%20the%20Study%20of%20Social%20Systems%2C%20School%20of%20Social%20Sciences%20in%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%2C%20Delhi.%20In%20an%20interview%2C%20he%20speaks%20about%20the%20need%20for%20state-based%20caste%20censuses%2C%20why%20governments%20must%20engage%20more%20with%20scholars%20to%20unpack%20caste%20data%2C%20and%20the%20need%20for%20subclassifications%20of%20SCs%2C%20STs%20and%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBCs).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3EEdited%20excerpts%3A%20%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3EWhy%20is%20it%20important%20to%20collect%20and%20collate%20all%20caste%20data%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20SC%2FST%20data%20in%20the%20population%20census%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ESince%20the%20early%201990s%2C%20caste%20has%20come%20to%20be%20accepted%20as%20a%20development%20variable.%20It%20has%20to%20be%20engaged%20by%20the%20state%20system%20actively.%20Caste%20is%20simply%20not%20a%20question%20of%20identity%2C%20but%20also%20an%20indicator%20of%20lack%20of%20development%2C%20exclusion%2C%20disability%20etc.%20So%2C%20the%20state%20cannot%20do%20without%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIndia%20recognises%20caste%20as%20an%20important%20indicator%20of%20social%20exclusions.%20The%20State%20should%20have%20been%20doing%20it%20%5Benumerating%20caste%5D%20on%20an%20extensive%20level.%20It%20is%20not%20about%20classifying%20communities%20as%20SC%2C%20ST%20and%20OBC%2C%20but%20we%20need%20to%20understand%20issues%20like%20employment%20and%20education%20like%20how%20Sachar%20Committee%20did%20with%20the%20available%20data%20on%20Muslims%20in%20India.%20It%20%5Black%20of%20quality%20data%5D%20becomes%20a%20bone%20of%20contention%20even%20in%20courts%20when%20there%20are%20petitions%20related%20to%20reservations%20and%20courts%20ask%20for%20caste%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%5BNote%3A%20Rajinder%20Sachar%20Committee%20%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.minorityaffairs.gov.in%2FWriteReadData%2FRTF1984%2F7830578798.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cu%3Ereport%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%20on%20the%20social%2C%20economic%20and%20educational%20status%20of%20Muslims%20in%20India%20was%20tabled%20in%20Parliament%20in%202006.%5D%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3ECaste%20data%20are%20nearly%20a%20century%20old.%20The%20demand%20for%20a%20caste%20census%20is%20now%20being%20used%20or%20projected%20politically%20to%20take%20on%20the%20narrative%20of%20cultural%20nationalism.%20How%20was%20colonial%20caste%20enumeration%20and%20administrative%20requirement%20different%20from%20the%20need%20to%20enumerate%20caste%20now%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EWe%20have%20a%20stereotype%20about%20caste%20based%20on%20the%20%3Ci%3Evarna%3C%2Fi%3E%20hierarchy%20that%20it%20is%20ancient%20and%20stable%2C%20and%20nothing%20changes.%20The%20reality%20of%20caste%20is%20different%20at%20the%20regional%20level.%20Caste%20is%20a%20living%20reality.%20There%20are%20differences%20between%20communities%20based%20on%20migration%20or%20land%20ownership.%20When%20you%20start%20looking%20at%20development%20and%20material%20variables%2C%20we%20find%20that%20caste%20is%20more%20than%20just%20ritual%20hierarchy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20notions%20that%20the%20colonial%20British%20government%20had%20was%20derived%20from%20classical%20Hindu%20texts.%20Reality%20of%20caste%20is%20local%20and%20fluid.%20It%20is%20linked%20to%20many%20issues%20like%20employment%20and%20land%20ownership.%20Urban%20economies%20are%20also%20structured%20around%20identities.%20Even%20if%20it%20is%20not%2C%20we%20need%20evidence%20to%20say%20so.%20We%20need%20extensive%20and%20systematic%20datasets%20to%20counter%20narratives%20around%20caste%2C%20which%20currently%20do%20not%20exist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EReservation%20has%20become%20a%20point%20of%20mobilisation.%20Underlying%20this%20are%20other%20anxieties.%20India%20is%20a%20neoliberal%20economy%20where%20employment%20is%20difficult%20for%20upwardly%20mobile%20communities%20that%20come%20from%20the%20margins.%20Even%20the%20tentative%20data%20that%20Bihar%20caste%20census%20has%20exposed%20privileges.%20It%20is%20not%20about%20backwardness%20or%20disadvantages.%20If%20certain%20top-end%20jobs%20are%20monopolised%20by%20few%20communities%2C%20it%20shows%20that%20those%20networks%20have%20monopolised%20it.%20It%20is%20called%20%E2%80%98opportunity%20hoarding%E2%80%99%20in%20sociology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20order%20to%20engage%20with%20these%20issues%20in%20a%20democratic%20society%2C%20we%20need%20empirical%20evidence.%20Unless%20there%20are%20political%20mobilisations%2C%20systems%20do%20not%20open%20up.%20It%20can%20also%20fossilise%20caste%20identities.%20The%20objective%20of%20caste%20census%20should%20not%20be%20to%20reinforce%20caste-based%20identity%20or%20an%20identity%20based%20imagination%20of%20our%20future.%20It%20should%20be%20made%20a%20part%20of%20a%20narrative%20around%20socioeconomic%20lives.%20Eventually%2C%20the%20hope%20is%20that%20once%20there%20is%20a%20level%20playing%20field%2C%20we%20can%20explore%20transforming%20identities%20into%20citizenship-based%20social%20life%20where%20everyone%20feels%20that%20they%20are%20equal%20to%20others.%20This%20requires%20evidence%20and%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3EBihar%20has%20shown%20that%20caste%20data%20can%20be%20collected%20and%20collated%20administratively.%20Despite%20the%20Registrar%20General%20and%20Census%20Commissioner%20of%20India%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsansad.in%2FgetFile%2Flsscommittee%2FRural%2520Development%2520and%2520Panchayati%2520Raj%2F16_Rural_Development_27.pdf%3Fsource%3Dloksabhadocs%23page%3D10%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3E%3Cu%3Esaying%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cb%3E%20that%2099%25%20religion%20and%20caste%20data%20in%20Socio-Economic%20Caste%20Census%20(SECC)%202011%20are%20%E2%80%9Cerror%20free%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20did%20not%20release%20SECC%202011%20caste%20data%2C%20collected%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20nearly%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsansad.in%2FgetFile%2Floksabhaquestions%2Fannex%2F14%2FAS245.pdf%3Fsource%3Dpqals%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3E%3Cu%3ERs%204%2C900%20crore%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cb%3E%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsansad.in%2FgetFile%2Fannex%2F254%2FAS244.pdf%3Fsource%3Dpqars%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3E%3Cu%3Edue%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cb%3E%20to%20%E2%80%9Ctechnical%20problems%E2%80%9D%20and%20because%20the%20data%20are%20%E2%80%9Cvery%20old%20and%20not%20useable%E2%80%9D.%20Is%20it%20difficult%20to%20comprehensively%20collect%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cb%3E%3Ci%3Ejati%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cb%3E%20(caste)%20data%20accurately%3F%20How%20do%20researchers%20and%20scholars%20like%20yourself%20come%20in%20to%20build%20on%20this%20data%20and%20unpack%20complexities%3F%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThis%20is%20critical.%20We%20need%20to%20learn%20from%20more%20than%20a%20century%20of%20scholarship%20on%20caste.%20When%20the%20colonial%20government%20started%20collecting%20caste%20data%2C%20they%20did%20not%20have%20any%20idea%20of%20the%20reality%20of%20caste.%20Caste%20formations%20are%20regional%20in%20character.%20The%20government%20needs%20to%20engage%20with%20scholars%20much%20more%20than%20it%20presently%20does.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20government%E2%80%99s%20understanding%20is%20that%20they%20know%20what%20caste%20is.%20We%20will%20go%20back%20to%20some%20notion%20of%20%3Ci%3Evarna%3C%2Fi%3E%20hierarchy%20or%20a%20corresponding%20hierarchical%20structure%20where%20communities%20will%20be%20fit%20into%20%3Ci%3Ekshatriya%2C%20vaishya%2C%20shudra%20or%20brahmin%20varna%3C%2Fi%3E.%20That%20needs%20to%20be%20abandoned.%20For%20example%2C%20in%20Haryana%2C%20where%20will%20you%20place%20Jats%3F%20They%20are%20not%20%3Ci%3Eshudra%2C%20kshatriya%2C%20vaishya%20or%20brahmin.%3C%2Fi%3E%20South%20India%20does%20not%20have%20communities%20that%20correspond%20to%20a%20vague%20%3Ci%3Ekshatriya%3C%2Fi%3E%20hierarchy%2C%20but%20that%20does%20not%20mean%20that%20there%20are%20communities%20that%20are%20not%20dominant%2C%20like%20Nairs%20who%20are%20ruling%20castes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EWe%20need%20caste%20commissions%20at%20the%20state%20level%20like%20we%20have%20state%20listings%20for%20SCs%2C%20STs%20and%20OBCs.%20We%20need%20state-specific%20datasets%20and%20data%20profiles.%20We%20can%20have%20broad%20categorisation%20after%20we%20have%20region-specific%20data%20on%20%3Ci%3Ejatis%20%3C%2Fi%3Eand%20%3Ci%3Eupjatis%20%3C%2Fi%3E(subcastes).%20Occupations%2C%20status%20and%20hierarchies%2C%20identities%20are%20all%20region-specific.%20We%20do%20not%20need%20comparative%20data%20at%20the%20national%20level%20for%20groups%2C%20but%20deprivation%20does%20exist.%20There%20may%20be%20communities%20who%20are%20deprived%20due%20to%20their%20caste%20background%20and%20there%20may%20be%20those%20who%20were%20privileged%20and%20may%20not%20be%20any%20longer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ETo%20achieve%20this%2C%20scholarship%20needs%20to%20be%20taken%20much%20more%20seriously%20and%20experts%20need%20to%20be%20included%20in%20commissions.%20The%20political%20elite%20picks%20these%20issues%20%5Bcaste%20census%5D%20to%20politically%20encash%20it%2C%20rather%20than%20being%20serious%20about%20it%20in%20the%20development%20process%20to%20bring%20caste%20for%20a%20citizenship%20project%20to%20materialise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3EEssentially%2C%20the%20task%20of%20enumerating%20and%20unpacking%20caste%20data%20must%20be%20done%20by%20states.%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EYes%2C%20this%20is%20the%20only%20way%20you%20can%20do%20caste%20data%20collection.%20You%20cannot%20have%20a%20national%20level%20schedule%20for%20caste.%20You%20can%20have%20it%20for%20age%2C%20family%2C%20gender%20etc.%20Even%20reservations%20are%20at%20a%20state%20level%20based%20on%20state-level%20lists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3EWhat%20type%20of%20challenges%20and%20fault%20lines%20does%20an%20enormous%20and%20complex%20task%20of%20enumeration%20of%20castes%20in%20India%20expose%3F%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThere%20is%20elite%20resistance%20on%20caste%20enumeration.%20It%20also%20reflects%20their%20bad%20faith.%20It%20is%20a%20fear%20that%20the%20data%20may%20expose%20that%20their%20proportions%20are%20much%20higher%20in%20positions%20of%20privilege.%20India%20continues%20to%20be%20a%20society%20where%20inequality%20is%20pervasive%20and%2C%20at%20some%20level%2C%20seen%20as%20legitimate.%20Some%20of%20it%20comes%20from%20caste%20and%20some%20from%20the%20idea%20of%20modernity%20where%20merit%20becomes%20a%20central%20feature.%20It%20goes%20beyond%20the%20political%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EPolitical%20representation%20may%20have%20improved%20for%20OBC%20communities%20due%20to%20their%20%5Blarger%5D%20numbers%20compared%20to%20SCs%2C%20but%20in%20the%20larger%20society%2C%20inequality%20remains.%20We%20have%20condos%20which%20cost%20crores%20of%20rupees%20while%20there%20are%20households%20which%20are%20making%20less%20than%20Rs%2010%2C000%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexplained%2Fexplained-law%2Flegal-debate-sub-categorisation-among-scheduled-castes-9117612%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3E%3Cu%3Ehearing%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cb%3E%20the%20case%20on%20subclassification%20of%20SCs%20and%20the%20power%20of%20states%20to%20modify%20reservations.%20There%20is%20diversity%20among%20caste%20groups%20within%20SC%2C%20ST%20and%20OBC.%20While%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressreleaseshare.aspx%3FPRID%3D1575533%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3E%3Cu%3EJustice%20(Retd.)%20G.%20Rohini%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cb%3E%20report%20on%20OBC%20sub-categorisation%20has%20been%20submitted%2C%20many%20states%20already%20have%20subcategories.%20How%20do%20you%20analyse%20the%20issue%20of%20determining%20sub-categories%20when%20census%20data%2C%20household%20consumption%20expenditure%20data%20and%20caste%20data%2C%20among%20others%20are%20unavailable%2C%20old%20or%20have%20quality%20issues%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20subclassification%20issue%20came%20up%20a%20decade%20ago.%20It%20is%20critical%20if%20caste%20has%20to%20become%20a%20development%20variable.%20SC%20or%20OBC%20are%20very%20broad%20administrative%20classification.%20Within%20SC%2C%20there%20are%20many%20communities%20across%20states%20but%20benefits%20have%20gone%20to%20few%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ESC%2C%20ST%20and%20OBC%20need%20to%20be%20subclassified.%20Without%20proper%20data%2C%20subclassification%20can%20only%20be%20done%20through%20political%20push%20and%20pull.%20There%20are%20lobbies%20within%20communities%20which%20need%20to%20be%20transcended%20politically.%20Subclassification%20should%20have%20happened%20long%20back%20and%20commissions%20should%20not%20sit%20on%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3ERecently%2C%20the%20Maharashtra%20government%2C%20through%20a%20notification%2C%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fcities%2Fmumbai%2Fmaharashtra-govt-issues-notification-to-recognise-as-kunbis-kin-of-marathas-whose-kunbi-caste-records-found%2Farticle67782485.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3E%3Cu%3Eextended%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cb%3E%20the%20scope%20of%20Kunbi%20OBC%20certification%20to%20the%20dominant%20Maratha%20community.%20This%20impacts%20OBC%20representation%20in%20the%20state.%20Caste%20identity-based%20mobilisation%20continues%20to%20be%20significant%20in%20India.%20Your%20comments%20on%20the%20use%20of%20caste%20data%20and%20consolidation%20of%20caste%20identities%20politically%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThere%20is%20no%20trust%20in%20the%20state%20system.%20If%20there%20was%20a%20transparent%20system%20of%20accountability%20which%20everyone%20subscribes%20to%2C%20these%20problems%20will%20not%20arise.%20If%20there%20are%20elections%2C%20Marathas%2C%20who%20are%20a%20large%20group%2C%20can%20mobilise%20and%20push%20their%20way%20into%20these%20%5Bstate%5D%20lists.%20This%20has%20happened%20in%20Punjab%20where%20communities%20who%20may%20not%20have%20faced%20untouchability%20pushed%20their%20way%20into%20the%20SC%20list.%20The%20SC%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.welfare.punjab.gov.in%2FStatic%2FSCPopulation.html%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Epopulation%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20state%20is%2032%25.%20While%20it%20is%20unfortunate%20that%20it%20is%20done%20for%20political%20gain%20by%20political%20parties%2C%20it%20helps%20us%20realise%20that%20the%20political%20process%20initiates%20the%20change.%20But%20the%20state%20needs%20to%20be%20more%20professional%20and%20transparent%20on%20such%20issues.%20Institutions%20in%20India%20do%20not%20function%20how%20they%20ideally%20should%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3ESo%2C%20for%20caste%20census%2C%20do%20you%20think%20we%20need%20a%20new%20institution%20that%20does%20caste-specific%20data%20collation%20every%20five%20or%2010%20years%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIf%20discussions%20happen%20in%20central%20and%20state%20legislatures%20and%20proposals%20are%20placed%20in%20the%20public%20sphere%20and%20thereon%20becomes%20law%2C%20it%20becomes%20acceptable.%20I%20remember%20the%20reaction%2C%20particularly%20within%20the%20Muslim%20community%20when%20the%20Sacchar%20committee%20report%20was%20released.%20It%20can%20happen%2C%20but%20our%20institutions%20have%20become%20weaker%20now.%20It%20makes%20people%20feel%20insecure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20has%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexplained%2Fexplained-who-are-pasmanda-muslims-bjp-pm-modi-8017276%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3E%3Cu%3Ereached%20out%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cb%3E%20to%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiaspend.com%2Findiaspend-interviews%2Fcaste-census-is-a-nation-building-exercise-808337%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3E%3Cu%3EPasmanda%20Muslims%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cb%3E%20and%20there%20is%20a%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tribuneindia.com%2Fnews%2Fnation%2Fquota-for-dalit-christians-and-muslims-supreme-court-wonders-if-rangnath-misra-panel-report-can-be-relied-upon-496743%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3E%3Cu%3Epetition%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cb%3E%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20include%20Dalit%20Christians%20and%20Muslims%20in%20SC%20category.%20Meanwhile%20the%20Congress%20has%20put%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Felections%2Flok-sabha%2Fcong-goes-slow-on-jitni-aabadi-utna-haq-catchline-after-cwc-meeting%2Farticleshow%2F104659706.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3E%3Cu%3Eforward%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cb%3E%20a%20slogan%20for%20entitlements%20proportional%20to%20caste%20population%20(%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cb%3E%3Ci%3Ejitni%20abadi%2C%20utna%20haq%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cb%3E).%20While%20caste%20in%20India%20is%20seen%20mostly%20from%20the%20prism%20of%20reservations%2C%20what%20shift%20is%20required%20to%20better%20understand%20caste%20identities%2C%20citizenship%20and%20development%2C%20and%20how%20can%20it%20be%20done%3F%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20question%20of%20Dalit%20Muslims%20and%20Christians%20is%20a%20much%20bigger%20issue%20and%20I%20do%20not%20think%20anything%20much%20will%20happen.%20The%20way%20our%20Constitution%20is%20framed%2C%20it%20does%20not%20allow%20reservations%20for%20Muslim%20and%20Christians.%20In%20some%20sense%2C%20it%20recognises%20caste%20as%20a%20Hindu%20institution.%20But%20they%20have%20been%20categorised%20under%20OBCs%20in%20some%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EDeveloping%20a%20system%20where%20identities%20do%20not%20get%20consolidated%2C%20and%20become%20a%20development%20variable%20is%20the%20biggest%20challenge.%20People%20are%20not%20going%20to%20give%20up%20their%20communities%20and%20identities.%20The%20effort%20should%20be%20towards%20citizenship%20building%20by%20providing%20job%20and%20education%20security%2C%20for%20example.%20We%20have%20stopped%20talking%20about%20such%20issues%20due%20to%20which%20identity%20becomes%20a%20refuge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ECaste%20associations%20have%20become%20more%20significant%20in%20small%20towns%20than%20they%20were%20a%20few%20decades%20ago.%20As%20anxieties%20increase%2C%20caste%20mobilisations%20make%20it%20easier%20to%20engage%20for%20groups.%20India%20is%20not%20the%20caste%20society%20it%20used%20to%20be%20earlier%2C%20but%20only%20credible%20institutions%20and%20democratic%20public%20dialogue%20can%20resolve%20these%20problems.%20It%20is%20not%20easy%20but%20also%20not%20impossible.%20It%20requires%20honest%20political%20will.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22italic%5C%22%3EThis%20story%20was%20first%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiaspend.com%2Findiaspend-interviews%2Fwe-need-extensive-systematic-datasets-to-counter-narratives-around-caste-894044%5C%22%3Epublished%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20%3C%2Fi%3EIndiaSpend%2C%20%3Ci%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22italic%5C%22%3Ea%20data-driven%2C%20public-interest%20journalism%20non-profit.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708097409000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16183610%2Fimage-1841.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fwe-need-extensive-systematic-datasets-to-counter-narratives-around-caste%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20notions%20that%20the%20colonial%20British%20government%20had%20was%20derived%20from%20classical%20Hindu%20texts%2C%20says%20sociologist%20Surinder%20Jodhka.%20Reality%20of%20caste%20is%20local%20and%20fluid%20and%20linked%20to%20many%20issues%20like%20employment%20and%20land%20ownership.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fwe-need-extensive-systematic-datasets-to-counter-narratives-around-caste%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%20Yulia%20Navalnaya%20speak%20following%20report%20of%20husband's%20death%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708096377000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F10D84%2Fproduction%2F_132669986_p0hcd2fy.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68319500%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Yulia%20Navalnaya%20tells%20a%20conference%20in%20Munich%20she%20doesn't%20know%20whether%20the%20%26quot%3Bhorrible%20news%26quot%3B%20is%20true.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A629%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fav%2Fworld-europe-68319500%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Ram%E2%80%99s%20Hailing%2C%20Sita%20Was%20Forgotten.%20Her%20Revival%20Would%20Have%20Symbolised%20Healing%20for%20Men%20and%20Women%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16175719%2Fimage-1840.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EReaders%C2%A0of%C2%A0the%C2%A0%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Eon%20January%2023%C2%A0might%20have%C2%A0overlooked%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0in%C2%A0the%20flood%C2%A0of%20Ram%20Mandir%20stories%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fpune%2Fsita-temple-in-maharashtra-that-farm-leader-sharad-joshi-envisaged-9121973%2F%5C%22%3Eone%20news%20item%3C%2Fa%3E%20tucked%20away%20in%20the%20interior%20pages.%20It%20talked%20about%20a%20small%20temple%20in%20the%20village%20of%20Raveri%20in%20Yavatmal%20district%2C%20the%20same%20region%20of%20Maharashtra%20where%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Valmiki%20%3Cem%3ERamayana%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Sita%20and%20her%C2%A0sons%20Luv%C2%A0and%20Kush%2C%C2%A0had%20spent%20their%20exile%20from%C2%A0Ayodhya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20article%20claims%20that%20it%20is%20the%20only%20Sita%20Temple%20in%20the%20whole%20of%20India.%20There%20had%20been%2C%20prior%20to%20the%20bulldozing%20of%20the%20ground%20in%20preparation%20for%20the%20new%20Ram%20Mandir%2C%20a%20building%20called%20%3Cem%3ESita%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3Es%20Kitchen.%3C%2Fem%3E%20But%20that%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20even%20a%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20spoken%2C%20after%C2%A0consecrating%C2%A0the%20Ram%20Statue%20in%20the%20new%20premises%2C%20of%20the%20need%20to%C2%A0create%20a%20Ram%20Rajya%20that%20embodies%20the%20virtues%20of%20a%20just%2C%20inclusive%20and%20compassionate%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20would%20have%20been%20befitting%20for%20an%20event%20which%20the%20present%20prime%20minister%20evoked%20in%20such%20terms%20and%20called%20a%20historic%20moment%2C%20to%20not%20only%20welcome%20back%20Ram%2C%20but%20also%20resurrect%20his%20consort.%20For%20far%20too%20long%20our%20Sitas%20have%20been%20buried%20under%20the%20furrows%20of%20the%20land%20to%20which%20she%20had%20retreated%20in%20order%20to%20save%20her%20honour%20as%20a%20wife%20and%20a%20woman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESita%E2%80%99s%20Sati%20had%20been%20a%20silent%20protest%20against%20the%20treatment%20meted%20out%20to%20her%20by%20her%20spouse%20and%20king.%20To%20many%20women%20in%20India%2C%20throughout%20its%20long%20history%2C%20Sita%20has%20been%20seen%20not%20only%20as%20the%20model%20wife%2C%20but%20also%20as%20the%20archetypal%20victim%20of%20a%20male-dominated%20world.%20To%20this%20day%2C%20male%20pre-eminence%20remains%20the%20societal%20norm%20reserved%20to%20men%2C%20best%20represented%20by%20the%20figure%20of%20King%20Ram%2C%20and%20sanctified%20by%20his%20assigned%20divine%20status.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEver%20since%20the%20constitution%20was%20established%20by%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20parliament%20%E2%80%93%20a%20document%20which%2C%20it%20is%20worth%20remembering%2C%20the%20current%20prime%20minister%20himself%20has%20called%20his%20%E2%80%98Gita%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20the%20equal%20rights%20of%20women%20have%20been%20enshrined%20and%20guaranteed.%20The%20foundation%20had%20thus%20been%20laid%20for%20a%20society%20that%20is%20neither%20patriarchal%20nor%20matriarchal%2C%20but%20based%20on%20the%20mutual%20respect%20of%20a%20shared%20citizenship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20symbolic%20framing%20of%20the%20inauguration%20of%20a%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98second%20Birth%20of%20the%20Nation%E2%80%99%2C%20this%20time%20not%20political%20but%20cultural%20and%20societal%20ruling%20elite%2C%20could%20have%20offered%20the%20chance%20to%20welcome%20back%20Sita%20as%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20queen%20alongside%20her%20spouse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20would%20have%20been%20even%20more%20befitting%20if%20one%20looks%20at%20the%20inthronisation%20of%20Ram%20in%20his%20child%20avatar%20as%20Ram%20Lalla%2C%20moreover%20at%20his%20very%20birthplace.%20Sita%E2%80%99s%20presence%20would%20have%20given%20due%20respect%20to%20the%20symbol%20of%20motherhood%20and%20to%20the%20essential%20role%20a%20mother%20plays%20in%20delivering%20a%20child%20and%20rearing%20it%20to%20full%20personhood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20not%20to%20be%2C%20and%20this%20erasure%20of%20constitutional%20Dharma%20reflects%20not%20only%20the%20male-dominated%20narrative%20of%20the%20whole%20Mandir%20movement%20and%20its%20apogee%20moment%2C%20the%20grand%20ceremony%20of%20January%2022%2C%202024.%20It%20also%20leads%20one%20to%20suspect%20(and%20fear!)%20that%20the%20Golden%20Future%20of%20Indian%20Society%20envisaged%20by%20the%20ruling%20elite%20remains%20trapped%20in%20the%20male-dominated%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20it%20is%20not%20only%20the%20legal%20code%20of%20the%20constitution%20which%20directs%20society%20%E2%80%93%20and%20its%20male%20flag%20bearers%20%E2%80%93%20to%20give%20up%20their%20predominant%20role.%20It%20is%20also%20a%20historical%20duty.%20For%20far%20too%20long%20Indian%20and%20indeed%20global%20society%20have%20lived%20by%20the%20negative%20values%20that%20are%20rooted%20in%20male%20psychology%20%E2%80%93%20those%20of%20power%20and%20authority%2C%20of%20rivalry%20and%20the%20language%20of%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20doubt%20in%20my%20mind%C2%A0that%C2%A0this%20one%20factor%20has%20brought%20the%20world%20to%20its%20present%C2%A0predicament%2C%C2%A0riven%20by%C2%A0constant%20wars%2C%C2%A0by%C2%A0systematic%20violence%20against%20nature%2C%20and%C2%A0a%20climate%20of%20suspicion%20and%20envy%2C%20of%20fear%20and%20hate%20among%20citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResurrecting%20Sita%20from%20her%20grave%20%E2%80%93%20especially%20after%20%E2%80%98unearthing%E2%80%99%20the%20very%20spot%20of%20her%20birth-giving%20as%20the%20spiritual%20fulcrum%20%E2%80%93%20would%20have%20been%20a%20powerful%20symbol%20of%20healing%20for%20both%20men%20and%20women%20of%20India.%20It%20would%20have%20put%20a%20spotlight%20on%20the%20shadows%20that%20besiege%20our%20society%2C%20proof%20of%20which%20can%20be%20seen%20in%20the%20fact%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20poets%20and%20folk%20tellers%20have%20constantly%20given%20it%20expression%20in%20the%20many%20versions%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3ERamayana%20Katha%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mere%20survival%2C%20viz.%20thriving%20of%20this%20myth%20through%20two%20millennia%2C%20is%20testimony%20enough%20that%20these%20shadows%20exist%2C%20and%20that%20they%20need%20to%20be%20looked%20at.%20To%20give%20this%20continuing%20erasure%20a%20symbolic%20focus%20point%2C%20Sita%20should%2C%20at%20the%20very%20least%2C%20be%20given%20a%20sacred%20place%20of%20redemption%20in%20her%20honour.%20A%20new%20peaceful%20and%20respectful%20movement%20should%20start%20%E2%80%93%20%3Cem%3Etoday%20for%20every%20Sita%20to%20rise%20in%20the%20hearts%20of%20every%20woman.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EJai%C2%A0Siyaram.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERashna%20Imhasly-Gandhy%20is%20a%20psychologist%20and%20author%20of%20the%20books%3C%2Fem%3E%20The%20Psychology%20of%20Love%20%E2%80%93%20Wisdom%20of%20Indian%20Mythology%20%3Cem%3Eand%3C%2Fem%3E%20The%20Emerging%20Feminine%20%E2%80%93%20discovering%20the%20Heroine%20Within.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708095657000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16175719%2Fimage-1840.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fin-rams-hailing-sita-was-forgotten-her-revival-would-have-symbolised-healing-for-men-and-women%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22To%20many%20women%20in%20India%2C%20Sita%20has%20been%20seen%C2%A0not%20only%20as%20the%20model%20wife%2C%20but%20also%C2%A0as%20the%20arc