0They%20advocate%20for%20the%20provision%20of%20pensions%20for%20both%20farmers%20and%20agricultural%20labourers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Swaminathan%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20findings%20underscore%20the%20stark%20economic%20realities%20faced%20by%20Indian%20farmers.%20In%202004%2C%20it%20found%20that%20an%20average%20Indian%20farming%20household%20earns%20a%20meagre%20income%20of%20only%20Rs%206%2C427%20per%20month%2C%20out%20of%20which%20a%20substantial%20portion%20%E2%80%93%20Rs%206%2C223%20%E2%80%93is%20spent%20on%20meeting%20essential%20expenses.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202022%20alone%2C%20data%20from%20the%20National%20Crime%20Records%20Bureau%20(NCRB)%20revealed%20a%20distressing%20statistic%3A%20on%20average%2C%20every%20hour%2C%20one%20farmer%20in%20India%20took%20their%20own%20life.%20This%20figure%20represented%20a%205.7%25%20increase%20compared%20to%202020.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20the%20standoff%20continues%2C%20with%20social%20media%20accounts%20silenced%20and%20farmers%20facing%20police%20action%2C%20the%20story%20is%20evolving%2C%20and%20we%20will%20continue%20to%20provide%20updates%20as%20events%20unfold.%20Watch%20this%20video%20to%20know%20more.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708093830000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16151513%2FSK9A0739.00_19_00_09.Still002.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fwatch-why-are-key-accounts-linked-to-the-farmers-protests-being-withheld%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20scenes%20at%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20borders%20remain%20tense%2C%20with%20a%20heavy%20police%20presence%20and%20barriers%20erected%20at%20Singhu%20and%20Ghazipur.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fwatch-why-are-key-accounts-linked-to-the-farmers-protests-being-with