e%20started%20growing%20water%20flowers%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20bought%20hardy%20water%20lilies%2C%20which%20was%20a%20mistake.%20The%20kind%20was%20not%20able%20to%20survive%20in%20the%20weather%20of%20Kerala%2C%20and%20all%20the%20plants%20died.%20But%20the%20whole%20process%20motivated%20me%20to%20try%20again%20as%20I%20was%20now%20curious%20and%20wanted%20to%20learn%20how%20they%20grow.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EViji%20not%20only%20learned%20the%20right%20way%20of%20growing%20lilies%2C%20she%20mastered%20it.%20Presently%2C%20she%20grows%20more%20than%20100%20varieties%20of%20lilies%20in%20her%20home%20garden.%20But%20that%20was%20also%20not%20enough%20for%20her%3B%20she%20wanted%20to%20hybridise%20her%20own%20variety!%20This%2C%20she%20thought%2C%20was%20a%20great%20way%20to%20fulfil%20her%20dream%20of%20contributing%20something%20creative%20to%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWith%20the%20help%20of%20the%20International%20Waterlily%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F250247%2Fgurugram-startup-bring-my-flowers-subscription-success-story-entrepreneur-delhi-small-biz-vid01%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWater%20Gardening%20%3C%2Fa%3ESociety%20and%20my%20fellow%20water%20lily%20planters%20on%20Facebook%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20hybridise%20my%20own%20variety.%20It%20is%20vibrant%20orange%20in%20colour%20and%20has%20the%20perfect%20number%20of%20petals.%20Nymphaea%20Sree%20meets%20the%20criteria%20of%20the%20experts%2C%20and%20hence%20the%20recognition%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EViji%20also%20learnt%20about%20the%20market%20demand%20for%20lilies.%20%E2%80%9CInitially%2C%20I%20did%20not%20know%20that%20lily%20plants%20fetch%20very%20good%20prices%20in%20the%20market.%20Later%20I%20started%20to%20sell%20my%20lilies%20through%20Facebook%20to%20people%20across%20the%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20successful%20